1
00:02:14,830 --> 00:02:15,400
什么?
What?

2
00:02:16,140 --> 00:02:17,420
希望渺茫?
A long shot?

3
00:02:17,420 --> 00:02:18,960
这个比赛吗?
This race?

4
00:02:21,790 --> 00:02:23,690
不能错过?
Can't miss?

5
00:02:23,690 --> 00:02:24,490
谢谢你,宝贝。
Thanks, baby.

6
00:02:24,490 --> 00:02:25,930
从零用现金中拿出两根胡萝卜。
Take two carrots out of petty cash.

7
00:02:25,930 --> 00:02:26,600
我和你核对一下。
I'll check with you.

8
00:02:26,600 --> 00:02:27,100
来吧，孩子。
Come on, kid.

9
00:02:27,100 --> 00:02:28,250
我们走吧。
Let's go.

10
00:02:28,250 --> 00:02:28,750
为什么?
Why?

11
00:02:28,750 --> 00:02:29,470
我在做什么?
What am I doing?

12
00:02:29,470 --> 00:02:30,390
兜售了。
Touting again.

13
00:02:30,390 --> 00:02:31,150
吹捧吗?
Touting?

14
00:02:31,150 --> 00:02:31,710
他吗?
Him?

15
00:02:31,710 --> 00:02:32,330
听着，孩子。
Now, listen, kid.

16
00:02:32,330 --> 00:02:34,120
我们看到你用了很多疯狂的方法。
We've seen you use some pretty wild schemes.

17
00:02:34,120 --> 00:02:34,620
为什么?
Why?

18
00:02:34,620 --> 00:02:37,220
这匹马碰巧喜欢吃柠檬汁，这是一种罪过吗?
Is it a crime this horse happens to have A sweet tooth for lemon drops?

19
00:02:37,220 --> 00:02:40,760
是啊，但你用这个对付那些疯狂的赛马玩家，他们会认为这匹马是在给你小费。
Yeah, but you're using this on these crazy horse players, They'll think the horse is giving you a tip.

20
00:02:40,760 --> 00:02:43,130
你知道，我知道，这匹马也知道。
Well, you know it and I know it and the horse knows it.

21
00:02:43,130 --> 00:02:45,350
但在法庭上听起来会很奇怪。
But it'll sound very peculiar in court.

22
00:02:45,350 --> 00:02:47,420
你就出格一次，小子。
Just step out of line once, Kid.

23
00:02:47,420 --> 00:02:48,530
手铐已经准备好了。
The handcuffs are ready.

24
00:02:48,530 --> 00:02:49,340
别再烦我了，好吗?
Lay off me, will you?

25
00:02:49,340 --> 00:02:51,140
如果幸运的话，我会给你买加水的冰块。
And if I get lucky, I'll buy you some ice with waters.

26
00:02:54,730 --> 00:02:59,410
回想一下，就在上周四，我接受了他的一条建议。
To think just last Thursday, I went for one of his tips.

27
00:02:59,410 --> 00:03:01,980
你也吗?
You, too?

28
00:03:01,980 --> 00:03:03,950
我告诉你，乔治，我预感到肉馅饼会出事。
I tell you, George, I've got a hunch on Mince Pie.

29
00:03:03,950 --> 00:03:07,940
记得那次你吃了那个女人的派，第二天你就不能去上班了，因为你生病了?
Remember that time you ate that woman's pie, And you couldn't go to work the next day because you were sick?

30
00:03:07,940 --> 00:03:09,320
办公室被闪电击中了。
And the office was struck by lightning.

31
00:03:09,320 --> 00:03:13,760
艾伦，那匹马不会因为名字叫肉馅饼就跑得更快的。
Ellen, that horse isn't going to run any faster Just because its name is Mince Pie.

32
00:03:13,760 --> 00:03:15,190
肉馅饼三岁时表现不错。
Mince Pie is a pretty good three-year-old.

33
00:03:15,190 --> 00:03:16,430
会赢得很多比赛。
Going to win a lot of races.

34
00:03:16,430 --> 00:03:17,850
也就是说，如果它的腿康复了。
That is, if its leg gets well.

35
00:03:17,850 --> 00:03:19,890
你……你觉得他的腿有问题吗?
You... you think there's something wrong with his leg?

36
00:03:19,890 --> 00:03:21,980
觉得呢?
Think?

37
00:03:21,980 --> 00:03:23,420
我是田径兽医。
I'm the track vet.

38
00:03:23,420 --> 00:03:29,630
这是"阴道前"感染在"联邦"区域，这…哦，韧带发炎了。
It's a "precastinary" infection of the "fedasorial" area, Which... oh, inflamed ligaments.

39
00:03:29,630 --> 00:03:32,960
想象一下，让一条坏腿的马去比赛。
Imagine allowing a horse to race with a bad leg.

40
00:03:32,960 --> 00:03:34,800
一半的马都该坐轮椅。
Half of these horses should be in wheelchairs.

41
00:03:34,800 --> 00:03:38,560
这是他们抢栏杆的唯一原因，这让他们有了依靠。
It's the only reason they fight for the rail, It gives them something to lean on.

42
00:03:38,560 --> 00:03:40,860
你相信吗，比赛中只有一匹健康的马?
Would you believe it, there's only one Sound horse in the race?

43
00:03:45,060 --> 00:03:46,500
医生吗?
Doctor?

44
00:03:46,500 --> 00:03:47,450
医生。
Doctor.

45
00:03:47,450 --> 00:03:47,950
嗯嗯?
Mm-hm?

46
00:03:47,950 --> 00:03:50,390
你说只有一匹马没病。
You said there was only one horse that wasn't sick.

47
00:03:50,390 --> 00:03:51,340
医生，请问是哪一个?
Please, Doc, which one?

48
00:03:51,340 --> 00:03:53,000
所有的信息都是机密的，知道吗?
All that information is confidential, you know?

49
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:55,080
有点像医生和病人之间的关系。
Sort of between doctor and patient.

50
00:03:55,080 --> 00:03:55,940
我们不会告诉任何人。
We wouldn't tell anybody.

51
00:03:55,940 --> 00:03:57,510
你可以和我们分享你的秘密。
You could share your secret with us.

52
00:03:57,510 --> 00:03:58,780
我们会和你分享我们的奖金。
And we'd share our winnings with you.

53
00:03:58,780 --> 00:03:59,850
哦不，求你了，求你了。
Oh no, please, please.

54
00:03:59,850 --> 00:04:01,220
那是不道德的。
That would be unethical.

55
00:04:01,220 --> 00:04:04,760
不过，如果比赛结束后，你愿意为诊所捐点东西吗?
However, if after the race, you'd Like to donate something to the clinic?

56
00:04:04,760 --> 00:04:07,450
我们太拥挤了，每张床上都有两匹马。
We're so overcrowded, we have two horses in every bed.

57
00:04:07,450 --> 00:04:08,830
哦，当然，我们会的。
Oh, certainly, we will.

58
00:04:08,830 --> 00:04:10,390
哪匹马感觉不错?
Uh, which horse feels well?

59
00:04:10,390 --> 00:04:15,510
如果我是个赌徒，我会认为S-I-X是个非常幸运的数字。
Well, if I were a betting man, I'd Consider S-I-X a very lucky number.

60
00:04:15,510 --> 00:04:16,590
骶髂关节……嘘。
S-I... Shh.

61
00:04:16,590 --> 00:04:18,510
好了，安静。
All right, shush.

62
00:04:18,510 --> 00:04:20,720
——S-I-X。-那是伦巴舞。
- S-I-X. - That's Rhumba Dancer.

63
00:04:20,720 --> 00:04:22,500
来吧，艾伦。
Come on, Ellen.

64
00:04:22,500 --> 00:04:23,250
谢谢你，医生。
Thank you, Doctor.

65
00:04:23,250 --> 00:04:24,640
你为你的职业增光。
You're a credit to your profession.

66
00:04:24,640 --> 00:04:25,630
哦，没什么。
Oh, ho, it's nothing.

67
00:04:40,570 --> 00:04:42,100
不好意思。
Uh, excuse me.

68
00:04:42,100 --> 00:04:46,380
请原谅我这么挤进来，我大老远从芝加哥飞过来就是为了看我哥哥的比赛。
Pardon me for crowding in, but I flew all the way from Chicago To see my brother ride this race.

69
00:04:46,380 --> 00:04:49,250
我第一次看到他骑冠军。
First time I get to see him ride a winner.

70
00:04:49,250 --> 00:04:51,840
他哥哥是个骑师。
His brother's a jockey.

71
00:04:51,840 --> 00:04:52,510
有趣的事情。
Funny thing.

72
00:04:52,510 --> 00:04:54,410
妈妈一直以为他会是个子高的那个。
Mom always thought he was going to be the tall one.

73
00:04:54,410 --> 00:04:56,810
你怎么知道你哥哥会赢?
How do you know your brother's going to win?

74
00:04:56,810 --> 00:05:00,460
有很多方法可以修好，除非他们想把东西弄歪。
Lots of ways it's fixed, unless they Try to pull something crooked.

75
00:05:00,460 --> 00:05:02,800
有时候，马也会自己做交易。
Sometimes, the horses make their own deals, too, you know.

76
00:05:02,800 --> 00:05:05,540
好吧，你弟弟叫什么名字?
Uh, well, uh, what's your brother's name?

77
00:05:05,540 --> 00:05:07,390
我们也要为他加油。
We'd like to cheer for him, too.

78
00:05:07,390 --> 00:05:09,110
如果你知道，你就知道是哪匹马了。
If you knew that, you'd know which horse.

79
00:05:09,110 --> 00:05:10,400
哦，你不会后悔的。
Oh, you won't be sorry.

80
00:05:10,400 --> 00:05:11,830
比赛结束后我会照顾你的。
I'll take care of you after the race.

81
00:05:11,830 --> 00:05:12,690
一大块。
A big chunk.

82
00:05:12,690 --> 00:05:13,190
哦。
Oh.

83
00:05:13,190 --> 00:05:16,450
我不是那么在乎钱。
Well, I don't care about the money so much.

84
00:05:16,450 --> 00:05:19,840
毕竟，你们看起来确实像正派人。
After all, you do look like decent people.

85
00:05:19,840 --> 00:05:22,500
数字是S-E-V-E-N。
The number is S-E-V-E-N.

86
00:05:22,500 --> 00:05:26,310
S-E-V-E-N。那是铁棒。
S-E-V-E-N. That's Iron Bar.

87
00:05:26,310 --> 00:05:28,800
我们真高兴能遇到你。
Oh, we're so glad we happened to meet you.

88
00:05:28,800 --> 00:05:29,810
你相信吗?
Would you believe it?

89
00:05:29,810 --> 00:05:31,750
这是我们今天赢的第一场比赛。
This is the first race we've won today.

90
00:05:31,750 --> 00:05:34,270
好吧,然后……哦,有…这是你哥哥。
Well, then... Oh, there... there's your brother now.

91
00:05:34,270 --> 00:05:35,910
嗯?
Hm?

92
00:05:35,910 --> 00:05:37,270
哦，嗨，杰瑞!
Oh, hi, Jerry!

93
00:05:37,270 --> 00:05:39,270
爸爸妈妈向你问好。
Mom and Dad send their love.

94
00:05:39,270 --> 00:05:40,000
祝你好运，孩子!
Lots of luck, kid!

95
00:05:44,450 --> 00:05:45,990
看到他怎么假装不认识我了吗?
See how he pretends not to know me?

96
00:05:45,990 --> 00:05:47,310
最聪明的小操作员。
Smartest little operator around.

97
00:05:55,810 --> 00:05:58,150
我告诉你，先生，我知道我们在圣诞节比赛。
I tell you, sir, I know we race Christmas Day.

98
00:05:58,150 --> 00:05:59,690
听着，孩子，我得确定。
Look, sonny, I got to be sure.

99
00:05:59,690 --> 00:06:02,600
现在，帮我去问问威尔金森法官。
Now, go ask Judge Wilkinson for me.

100
00:06:11,950 --> 00:06:12,740
嗯嗯。
Mm-hm.

101
00:06:12,740 --> 00:06:15,070
他们还在印美元，是吧?
They're still printing dollars, huh?

102
00:06:16,210 --> 00:06:17,940
哦，你说什么，女士?
Oh, I beg your pardon, ma'am?

103
00:06:17,940 --> 00:06:19,220
你们都在跟我说话?
Y'all addressing me?

104
00:06:19,220 --> 00:06:22,540
好吧，亲爱的孩子，你是不是把这5美元掉在地上了?
Well, honey child, Did y'all just dropped this $5 bill?

105
00:06:22,540 --> 00:06:23,880
哦,我……我不可能。
Oh, I... I couldn't have.

106
00:06:23,880 --> 00:06:25,390
我的都是百位。
Mine are all hundreds.

107
00:06:25,390 --> 00:06:26,190
是的，我的也是。
Yeah, mine, too.

108
00:06:26,190 --> 00:06:27,680
它一定是某个北方佬的。
It must belong to some Yankee.

109
00:06:27,680 --> 00:06:30,130
你们一定很幸运，因为你们很漂亮。
Well, y'all must be as lucky as you are beautiful.

110
00:06:30,130 --> 00:06:32,750
我的绅士朋友把这一切都押在了铁棒上。
My gentleman friend is betting all this on Iron Bar.

111
00:06:32,750 --> 00:06:33,680
铁酒吧?
Iron Bar?

112
00:06:33,680 --> 00:06:36,340
好吧，玉米饼和猪肠!
Well, corn my pone and chit my chitlins!

113
00:06:36,340 --> 00:06:40,970
我本来打算自己在那匹马身上留下一个漂亮的身材，直到我叔叔告诉我比赛已经安排好了。
I was going to drop a handsome figure on that animal Myself until my uncle told me the race was fixed.

114
00:06:40,970 --> 00:06:41,600
你的叔叔吗?
Your uncle?

115
00:06:41,600 --> 00:06:42,110
是的。
Yeah.

116
00:06:42,110 --> 00:06:43,160
那是威尔金森法官。
Well, that's Judge Wilkinson.

117
00:06:43,160 --> 00:06:46,400
他是赛马俱乐部的头牌，也是终点线的主审。
He's the president of the Turf Club, And also, the head judge of the finish line.

118
00:06:46,400 --> 00:06:48,130
我现在只是在等他点头。
I'm just waiting now for him to give me the nod.

119
00:06:48,130 --> 00:06:50,230
当然，他是在调查。
He's investigating, of course.

120
00:06:50,230 --> 00:06:52,560
我的，首席裁判!
My, head judge!

121
00:06:52,560 --> 00:06:53,300
这是他。
That's him.

122
00:06:53,300 --> 00:06:54,470
有漂亮女孩的那个。
The one with the pretty girl.

123
00:06:54,470 --> 00:06:57,480
他给了我1美元问你圣诞节那天我们是否比赛。
He gives me $1 to ask you if we race on Christmas Day.

124
00:06:57,480 --> 00:06:59,270
他不相信我的话。
He won't take my word for it.

125
00:06:59,270 --> 00:06:59,990
一定是个游客。
Must be a tourist.

126
00:07:08,730 --> 00:07:12,640
好吧，如果比赛注定铁棒会输，你必须知道谁会赢。
Well, if the race is fixed for Iron Bar to lose, You must know who's going to win.

127
00:07:12,640 --> 00:07:15,110
是啊，但我不能泄露那样的信息。
Yeah, but I couldn't divulge information Like that.

128
00:07:15,110 --> 00:07:16,110
我发过誓要保守秘密。
I've been sworn to secrecy.

129
00:07:16,110 --> 00:07:19,060
我以南方真正绅士的身份发誓。
I gave my word as a true gentleman of the South.

130
00:07:19,060 --> 00:07:22,030
我对着一堆黑眼豌豆和蜜饯山药发誓。
I swore on a stack of black eyed peas and candied yams.

131
00:07:22,030 --> 00:07:23,350
这封邮件已被绑定。
This message had been binded.

132
00:07:23,350 --> 00:07:25,410
这里有两千现金。
There's two thousand cash-money here.

133
00:07:25,410 --> 00:07:28,300
我的绅士朋友会在比赛结束后好好照顾你的。
My gentleman friend would take good care of you After the race.

134
00:07:28,300 --> 00:07:30,420
好吧，祝福你的心，亲爱的孩子。
Well, bless your heart, honey child.

135
00:07:30,420 --> 00:07:35,010
号码是E-I-G-H，你们都是T。
Uh, the number is, uh, E-I-G-H, y'all, T.

136
00:07:35,010 --> 00:07:36,390
你是说闪电侠?
You mean Lightning Streak?

137
00:07:36,390 --> 00:07:37,320
没有其他。
None other.

138
00:07:37,320 --> 00:07:38,110
谢谢你，先生。
Thank you, sir.

139
00:07:38,110 --> 00:07:40,390
比赛结束后，我们在生菜柜台见。
Uh, after the race, I'll meet you at the lettuce counter.

140
00:07:40,390 --> 00:07:40,960
我们会解决的。
We'll settle up.

141
00:07:40,960 --> 00:07:42,290
你们理解。
Y'all understand.

142
00:07:42,290 --> 00:07:43,250
闪电!
Lightning Streak!

143
00:07:47,950 --> 00:07:48,450
嘿,小子。
Hey, kid.

144
00:07:48,450 --> 00:07:49,790
你要大展拳脚了吗?
You getting on the big time?

145
00:07:49,790 --> 00:07:50,790
我在扩大我的生意。
I'm expanding my business.

146
00:07:50,790 --> 00:07:52,860
我要扩展到100美元的窗口。
I'm branching into the hundred-dollar window.

147
00:07:52,860 --> 00:07:54,180
你拿到那些战利品了吗?
Did you get a load of that loot?

148
00:07:54,180 --> 00:07:56,000
有个西红柿和她自己的卷心菜块。
There's a tomato with her own cabbage patch.

149
00:07:56,000 --> 00:07:56,660
两个G的!
Two G's!

150
00:07:56,660 --> 00:07:57,160
嗯嗯。
Mm-hm.

151
00:07:57,160 --> 00:07:57,830
噢!
Ow!

152
00:07:57,830 --> 00:07:58,880
你想要什么?
What do you expect?

153
00:07:58,880 --> 00:08:00,950
穆斯·莫兰总是下大赌注。
Moose Moran always bets heavy.

154
00:08:00,950 --> 00:08:02,660
驼鹿莫兰吗?
Moose Moran?

155
00:08:02,660 --> 00:08:04,450
你是说那个娃娃是穆斯·莫兰的?
You mean that doll belongs to Moose Moran?

156
00:08:04,450 --> 00:08:05,490
你不知道?
You didn't know it?

157
00:08:05,490 --> 00:08:07,180
嘿，你最好确定你给了他一个赢家。
Hey, you better be sure you gave him a winner.

158
00:08:07,180 --> 00:08:07,500
一个胜利者吗?
A winner?

159
00:08:07,500 --> 00:08:08,680
我分不清一匹马和另一匹马。
I don't know one horse from another.

160
00:08:08,680 --> 00:08:11,170
我最好抓住她，告诉她手术结束了，让她换电话号码。说…
I better grab her and tell her the fix is off, have her change Her number. Say...

161
00:08:14,320 --> 00:08:15,550
他们走了!
There they go!

162
00:08:15,550 --> 00:08:17,500
铁棒领先了。
It's Iron Bar taking the lead.

163
00:08:17,500 --> 00:08:18,480
闪电。
Lightning Streak.

164
00:08:18,480 --> 00:08:19,450
你在哪里?
Where are you?

165
00:08:19,450 --> 00:08:21,380
你想双手沾上我的血。
You want my blood on your hands.

166
00:08:21,380 --> 00:08:21,880
闪电!
Lightning!

167
00:08:21,880 --> 00:08:26,270
闪电闪电以11比7领先杆位。
Lightning Streak is 11 to 7 to pole.

168
00:08:26,270 --> 00:08:30,680
爸爸，我遇到了最好的男人。
Daddy, I met the nicest man.

169
00:08:30,680 --> 00:08:33,920
我给了你两千块赌铁棒。
I gave you two grand to bet on Iron Bar.

170
00:08:33,920 --> 00:08:35,390
我知道，但铁棒没机会了。
I know, but Iron Bar doesn't have a chance.

171
00:08:35,390 --> 00:08:37,440
