348
00:16:27,850 --> 00:16:29,390
天啊，见到你真高兴。
Boy, am I glad to see you.

349
00:16:29,390 --> 00:16:31,350
哦，我很高兴见到你。
Oh, and am I glad to see you.

350
00:16:31,350 --> 00:16:33,040
你来得正是时候，小子。
You're just in time, Kid.

351
00:16:35,900 --> 00:16:38,100
这是佛罗里达最新的东西…比基尼毛衣。
It's the newest thing in Florida... the bikini sweater.

352
00:16:38,100 --> 00:16:40,960
制作它的女孩给我签了名。
The gal that made it autographed it for me.

353
00:16:40,960 --> 00:16:42,890
汪,汪。
Woof, woof.

354
00:16:42,890 --> 00:16:46,270
孩子，我欠伊根先生钱。
Kid, I owe Mr. Egan some money.

355
00:16:46,270 --> 00:16:48,510
你还记得你欠我的20美元吗?
You remember that twenty dollars you owe me?

356
00:16:48,510 --> 00:16:50,600
什么，可怜的20美元?
What, a measly twenty dollars?

357
00:16:50,600 --> 00:16:53,930
我不仅记得这20，我还会把它还上，然后乘以20。
And I not only remember the twenty, I'm gonna pay it back and multiply it by twenty.

358
00:16:53,930 --> 00:16:57,000
够她付我四个月的房租了，还有一些。
That'll take care of the four months' rent she owes me, And then some.

359
00:16:57,000 --> 00:16:58,500
你别插手。
You keep out of this.

360
00:16:58,500 --> 00:17:00,450
听着，内莉，借我十块钱，好吗?
Listen, Nellie, lend me ten dollars, will you?

361
00:17:00,450 --> 00:17:02,670
这样我就能把冬天的衣服拿回来了?
So I can get my winter clothes out of hock?

362
00:17:02,670 --> 00:17:05,530
我不能穿成这样去雪莉和丽兹见我的朋友。
I can't go see my friends at the Sherry And the Ritz looking like this.

363
00:17:05,530 --> 00:17:08,060
他们会问我一些我不知道答案的问题。
They'd ask me questions for which I'm out of answers.

364
00:17:08,060 --> 00:17:11,420
孩子，你知道你在丽兹没有朋友。
Kid, you know you have not any friends at the Ritz.

365
00:17:11,420 --> 00:17:12,910
内莉，你怎么能这么说?
Nellie, how can you say that?

366
00:17:12,910 --> 00:17:14,200
你知道的。
You know I have.

367
00:17:14,200 --> 00:17:16,680
为什么有…手不对。
Why there's... uh, wrong hand.

368
00:17:16,680 --> 00:17:22,530
嗯，有，呃，呃…别担心，我会把钱还给你的。
Well, there's, uh, uh... don't worry, I'll give you the money back.

369
00:17:22,530 --> 00:17:24,730
6点前拿到。
Get it by 6 o'clock.

370
00:17:24,730 --> 00:17:28,930
这样你就有时间占领孤儿院了。
That'll give you time to dispossess an orphanage.

371
00:17:28,930 --> 00:17:32,410
你知道吗，内莉，如果我有内裤，我会把我身上的衬衫都给你。
You know, Nellie, I'd give you the shirt off my back If I had any underwear on.

372
00:17:32,410 --> 00:17:33,370
当然,孩子。
Sure, Kid.

373
00:17:33,370 --> 00:17:34,810
我知道。
I know that.

374
00:17:34,810 --> 00:17:36,250
不只是我。
It's not just for me.

375
00:17:36,250 --> 00:17:37,210
是给我丈夫的。
It's for my husband.

376
00:17:37,210 --> 00:17:39,460
你还记得我丈夫亨利吗?
You remember my husband, Henry?

377
00:17:39,460 --> 00:17:40,950
谁不喜欢呢?
Well, who doesn't?

378
00:17:40,950 --> 00:17:42,900
31年的新新班。
Sing Sing Class of '31.

379
00:17:42,900 --> 00:17:45,710
这是业界最棒的保险箱小撬。
Greatest little safe cracker in the business.

380
00:17:45,710 --> 00:17:48,620
亨利二十年后就要假释了。
Henry's getting paroled after twenty years.

381
00:17:48,620 --> 00:17:50,080
他平安夜出狱。
He gets out Christmas Eve.

382
00:17:50,080 --> 00:17:51,570
平安夜出去?
Gets out Christmas Eve?

383
00:17:51,570 --> 00:17:53,400
圣诞夜。
Christmas Eve.

384
00:17:53,400 --> 00:17:54,970
我可能见不到他了。
I may not be around to see him.

385
00:17:54,970 --> 00:17:59,050
但我会的，这样我就可以告诉他我们没地方住了。
But I will, so I can tell him how we got no place to stay.

386
00:17:59,050 --> 00:18:02,400
是啊，那你和亨利要搬去的那个老人院呢?
Yeah, well, what happened to that old folks' home That you and Henry were moving in?

387
00:18:02,400 --> 00:18:04,770
是的，阳光之家。
Yes, Sunshine Home, huh.

388
00:18:04,770 --> 00:18:09,120
他们拒绝了我的申请…都是为了亨利。
Well, they turned down my application... All on account of Henry.

389
00:18:09,120 --> 00:18:11,840
他们不会收有前科的人。
They won't take an ex-convict.

390
00:18:11,840 --> 00:18:17,770
下次探访日，我会告诉亨利待在原地不动。
Come next visiting day, I'm going To tell Henry to stay right where he is.

391
00:18:17,770 --> 00:18:20,760
至少，那里是暖和的。
At least, it's warm up there.

392
00:18:20,760 --> 00:18:22,760
即。
Brr.

393
00:18:22,760 --> 00:18:24,760
论文!
Papers!

394
00:18:24,760 --> 00:18:27,750
后期文件!
Late files!

395
00:18:27,750 --> 00:18:28,650
坚持住，内莉。
Stay with it, Nellie.

396
00:18:28,650 --> 00:18:29,490
振作起来。
Keep your chins up.

397
00:18:29,490 --> 00:18:30,580
总会有办法的。
Something will work out.

398
00:18:30,580 --> 00:18:32,210
嗯，也许是这样。
Well, maybe so.

399
00:18:32,210 --> 00:18:36,620
我遇到过比这更糟糕的困境。
I've been in worst jams than this.

400
00:18:36,620 --> 00:18:38,340
至少，你不再孤单了。
At least, you're not alone anymore, anyway.

401
00:18:42,270 --> 00:18:42,900
回头见。
I'll see you.

402
00:18:57,670 --> 00:19:08,870
图特·肖尔、波莉·特里、d·科拉、潘乔·欧·德怀尔、格罗弗·威廉、戈德堡、托尼·伯克……巴克斯特Brainey。
Toot Shore, Polly Terry, D. Cora, Pancho O'Dwyer, Grover William, Goldberg, Tony Burke... Brainey Baxter.

403
00:19:08,870 --> 00:19:12,280
啊，她还住在这里。
Ah, she still lives here.

404
00:19:12,280 --> 00:19:12,780
即。
Brr.

405
00:19:16,670 --> 00:19:19,230
你们得靠自己了，伙计们。
You're on your own, fellas.

406
00:19:19,230 --> 00:19:19,730
《银河系漫游指南》。
Hitchhiker.

407
00:19:24,310 --> 00:19:30,460
嗯，嗯，嗯，嗯，嗯。
Rrrh, mm, hmm, hmm, hmm.

408
00:19:31,950 --> 00:19:32,950
嗯,嗯。
Hmm, hmm.

409
00:19:37,420 --> 00:19:38,790
我以前从没见过它开花。
I never saw it bloom before.

410
00:19:41,850 --> 00:19:42,990
啊，还能用。
Ah, still works.

411
00:20:59,770 --> 00:21:02,700
如果你必须死，那是什么罪啊。
What a crime if you had to die.

412
00:21:07,970 --> 00:21:11,420
哦，一个花花公子。
Oh, a dandy.

413
00:21:21,270 --> 00:21:22,320
人力资源管理。
Hrm.

414
00:21:22,320 --> 00:21:26,280
我讨厌离开你，但这是命运!
I hate to leave you, but that's fate!

415
00:21:26,280 --> 00:21:28,240
哦，你这个娃娃，你!
Oh, you doll, you!

416
00:21:32,330 --> 00:21:33,160
Brainey !
Brainey!

417
00:21:37,590 --> 00:21:40,050
Brainey !
Brainey!

418
00:21:41,530 --> 00:21:44,480
Brainey !
Brainey!

419
00:21:45,490 --> 00:21:46,330
Brainey !
Brainey!

420
00:21:50,790 --> 00:21:52,570
布雷尼，你这个漂亮的娃娃，你!
Brainey, you gorgeous doll, you!

421
00:21:52,570 --> 00:21:53,980
你迟到了，小子。
You're late, Kid.

422
00:21:53,980 --> 00:21:56,080
我一到城里就过来了。
Oh, I came over as soon as I hit town.

423
00:21:56,080 --> 00:21:57,480
迟了六个月。
Six months late.

424
00:21:57,480 --> 00:21:58,630
你拿走了我的外套。
You left with my coat.

425
00:21:58,630 --> 00:22:00,400
你本来要帮我当掉的。
You were going to pawn it for me.

426
00:22:00,400 --> 00:22:02,830
我在等你回来。
I waited for you to come back.

427
00:22:02,830 --> 00:22:03,810
是这样的。
Well, it's like this.

428
00:22:03,810 --> 00:22:05,900
我正拿着你的钱回来。
I was on my way back with your money right in my hand.

429
00:22:05,900 --> 00:22:08,270
突然，我听说佛罗里达有一笔大生意。
All at once, I heard about a big deal in Florida.

430
00:22:08,270 --> 00:22:11,150
我想你在佛罗里达不需要皮大衣。
Well, I figured you won't need a fur coat in Florida.

431
00:22:11,150 --> 00:22:13,430
你去了佛罗里达，我留在这里。
You went to Florida, I stayed here.

432
00:22:13,430 --> 00:22:14,440
哦,Brainey。
Oh, Brainey.

433
00:22:14,440 --> 00:22:16,570
用这件大衣偿还我欠你的钱是轻而易举的事。
Squaring the money I owe you in the coat is a cinch.

434
00:22:16,570 --> 00:22:18,650
我刚在迈阿密发了财。
I just struck it rich in Miami.

435
00:22:18,650 --> 00:22:19,980
嗯，你看起来很像。
Mm, you look it.

436
00:22:19,980 --> 00:22:21,290
哦，你不明白。
Oh, you don't understand.

437
00:22:21,290 --> 00:22:26,480
我和一些有钱的朋友在赛马场，我想到了我爱的女人…也就是你，布莱尼·巴克斯特。
I'm out at the racetrack with some wealthy friends, And I get to thinking about the woman I love... meaning you, Brainey Baxter.

438
00:22:26,480 --> 00:22:28,050
当然，我不会等着改变。
Naturally, I don't wait to change.

439
00:22:28,050 --> 00:22:29,410
我赶了第一班飞机回家。
I grabbed the first plane home.

440
00:22:29,410 --> 00:22:31,350
我的行李在路上。
My luggage is on the way.

441
00:22:31,350 --> 00:22:35,210
如果迈阿密很胖，你怎么走得这么急?
If Miami is fat, how come you left in such a hurry?

442
00:22:35,210 --> 00:22:38,800
哦，呃，有一匹马叫婚礼仪式…赢得第二场比赛。
Oh, uh, there's a horse named Wedding Ceremony... wins the second race.

443
00:22:38,800 --> 00:22:40,130
婚礼，这是预感。
Wedding Ceremony, that's a hunch.

444
00:22:40,130 --> 00:22:43,570
除了你和我，谁都有可能。
It could mean nobody but you and I.

445
00:22:43,570 --> 00:22:44,800
现在，看，小子。
Now, look, Kid.

446
00:22:44,800 --> 00:22:46,460
我记得你是怎么操作的。
I remember how you operate.

447
00:22:46,460 --> 00:22:47,880
没有限制。
No holds barred.

448
00:22:47,880 --> 00:22:51,490
现在，我们不要谈论婚礼除非你是诚实的。
Now, let's not talk about a wedding ceremony Unless you're on the level.

449
00:22:51,490 --> 00:22:53,620
我不怪你不信任我，布雷尼。
Oh, I don't blame you for not trusting me, Brainey.

450
00:22:53,620 --> 00:22:55,770
有时候我不相信自己。
Sometimes I have days when I don't trust me.

451
00:22:55,770 --> 00:22:58,170
但为了配得上你，我愿意做任何事。
But I'll do anything to be worthy of you.

452
00:22:58,170 --> 00:23:01,360
说不定还能找到工作。
Might even get a job.

453
00:23:01,360 --> 00:23:04,020
婚礼和工作?
A wedding ceremony and a job?

454
00:23:04,020 --> 00:23:06,040
这是今年最伟大的一次冒险。
That's the greatest long shot parlay of the year.

455
00:23:06,040 --> 00:23:06,540
是的。
Yeah.

456
00:23:06,540 --> 00:23:09,510
我真希望我没把钱包落在我的新羊绒裤子里。
I just wish I hadn't left my wallet in my new cashmere Slacks.

457
00:23:09,510 --> 00:23:12,650
等我的衣服一到，我就带十块钱去拿驾照。
As soon as my clothes arrive, I'll take ten bucks and go right down And get a license.

458
00:23:12,650 --> 00:23:14,230
这就告诉你了。
That'll show you.

459
00:23:14,230 --> 00:23:15,590
我有十块钱。
I've get ten bucks.

460
00:23:15,590 --> 00:23:16,090
是吗?
Yeah?

461
00:23:19,380 --> 00:23:20,910
我说你是在虚张声势，小子。
I'm calling your bluff, Kid.

462
00:23:20,910 --> 00:23:22,970
我们现在就能拿到执照。
We can get the license right now.

463
00:23:22,970 --> 00:23:25,590
哦,娃娃!
Oh, doll!

464
00:23:25,590 --> 00:23:27,030
我马上去执照局。
I'll be right down to the license bureau.

465
00:23:27,030 --> 00:23:27,570
哦,等等!
Oh, wait!

466
00:23:27,570 --> 00:23:28,500
我要穿什么东西了。
I'll slip into something.

467
00:23:28,500 --> 00:23:29,600
哦，不要，不要。
Oh, don't, no.

468
00:23:29,600 --> 00:23:30,990
你不需要一起去。
No need you going along.

469
00:23:30,990 --> 00:23:33,080
你留在这里，把这里收拾好。
You stay here and fix up this place.

470
00:23:33,080 --> 00:23:34,580
记住，这是我们的蜜月小屋。
Remember, this is our honeymoon cottage.

471
00:23:34,580 --> 00:23:37,280
有很多香槟和五彩纸屑，是吧?
Get a lot of champagne and confetti, huh?

472
00:23:37,280 --> 00:23:38,530
就站在那里，就像这样。
And just stand there, just like that.

473
00:23:38,530 --> 00:23:40,520
漂亮!
Beautiful!

474
00:23:40,520 --> 00:23:43,020
一路走到市区，我想记住你的微笑。
All the way downtown, I want to remember you smiling.

475
00:23:46,920 --> 00:23:49,020
但我们都得去领执照。
But we both have to appear for a license.

476
00:23:49,020 --> 00:23:51,880
嘿，小子，等等!
Hey, Kid, wait!

477
00:23:56,160 --> 00:23:59,250
我的十块钱。
My ten bucks.

478
00:23:59,250 --> 00:24:01,610
他又这样做了。
He did it again.

479
00:24:09,710 --> 00:24:10,620
团聚,伙计们。
Reunion, fellas.

480
00:24:13,490 --> 00:24:14,440
Hrrrm。
Hrrrm.

481
00:24:17,890 --> 00:24:20,600
糊，糊，糊，糊!
Mush, mush, mush, mush!

482
00:24:30,280 --> 00:24:34,980
查理先生，根据我们的数据，你欠31400美元。
Mr. Charlie, according to our figures, You owe the government $31,400.

483
00:24:34,980 --> 00:24:39,290
你是说，我付的保护费不能扣减吗?
You mean to say, all that dough I Paid for protection isn't deductible?

484
00:24:39,290 --> 00:24:44,080
那笔钱只是…你想要什么?
Well, that money is just... what do you want?

485
00:24:44,080 --> 00:24:46,340
嗯，我只是路过。
Well, I was just passing by.

486
00:24:46,340 --> 00:24:49,250
我想去看看我的老朋友牛津·查理。
Thought I'd drop in to see my old pal Oxford Charlie.

487
00:24:49,250 --> 00:24:50,410
你好吗?
How are you?

488
00:24:50,410 --> 00:24:51,800
你的脚怎么样了?
How's your feet?

489
00:24:51,800 --> 00:24:53,260
他们要杀了我。
They're killing me.

490
00:24:53,260 --> 00:24:55,230
你来这儿干什么?给予还是得到?
What are you here for... Giving or getting?

491
00:24:55,230 --> 00:24:58,300
查理，我要跟你分一杯羹。
Oh, Charlie, I'm cutting you in on a solid gold deal.

492
00:24:58,300 --> 00:25:00,900
你可以用你那份利润穿貂皮牛津鞋了。
You'd be able to wear ermine oxfords With your share of the profits.

493
00:25:00,900 --> 00:25:02,990
你只要拿出一万现金就行了。
All you have to put up is ten grand in cash.

494
00:25:02,990 --> 00:25:03,770
这就够了。
That's enough.

495
00:25:03,770 --> 00:25:05,010
把面包屑扔出去。
Throw the crumb out.

496
00:25:05,010 --> 00:25:07,990
但你只需要种上区区一万美元，就能收获一大笔钱!
But all you have to do is plant a measly ten grand, And you harvest a fortune!

497
00:25:07,990 --> 00:25:08,650
把他扔出去。
Throw him out.

498
00:25:08,650 --> 00:25:10,380
我所得税的麻烦还不够多吗?
Ain't I got enough trouble with income tax?

499
00:25:10,380 --> 00:25:11,620
哦，但是，查理!
Oh, but, Charlie!

500
00:25:11,620 --> 00:25:14,030
牛津，我欠穆斯·莫兰一万美元。
Listen, Oxford, I owe Moose Moran ten grand.

501
00:25:14,030 --> 00:25:16,760
要么他在圣诞夜收到，要么我在圣诞节早上收到。
Either he gets it Christmas Eve or I get it Christmas morning.

502
00:25:16,760 --> 00:25:17,730
把钱借给我，好吗?
Lend me the dough, will you?

503
00:25:17,730 --> 00:25:18,660
你知道慕斯会做什么。
You know what Moose will do.

504
00:25:18,660 --> 00:25:20,730
我就会穿着水泥泳衣被扔进河里。
I'll wind up in the river with a cement bathing suit.

505
00:25:20,730 --> 00:25:21,980
我来供应水泥。
I'll supply the cement.

506
00:25:21,980 --> 00:25:22,480
出去!
Out!

507
00:25:22,480 --> 00:25:29,740
哦，但是，查理，我…查……我留下我的电话号码以防你改变主意?
Oh, but, Charlie, I... Cha... I'll leave my phone number In case you change your mind, huh?

508
00:25:29,740 --> 00:25:32,800
对不起，哦!
I'm sorry, oh!

509
00:25:32,800 --> 00:25:33,630
共产主义!
Communist!

510
00:25:35,120 --> 00:25:37,110
帮助有需要的人!
Help the needy!

511
00:25:37,110 --> 00:25:41,580
帮助有需要的人!
Help the needy!

512
00:25:41,580 --> 00:25:43,540
帮助有需要的人。
Help the needy.

513
00:25:43,540 --> 00:25:45,910
往锅里放点东西?
Put something in the pot?

514
00:25:45,910 --> 00:25:49,530
哦，至少你有一个。
Oh, at least, you've got one.

515
00:25:49,530 --> 00:25:51,320
帮助……谢谢您，先生。
Help... thank you, sir.

516
00:25:51,320 --> 00:25:54,040
帮助有需要的人!
Help the needy!

517
00:25:54,040 --> 00:25:55,040
谢谢你，女士。
Thank you, lady.

518
00:25:55,040 --> 00:25:56,880
帮助有需要的人!
Help the needy!

519
00:25:56,880 --> 00:25:58,240
帮助……谢谢你！
Help... thank you.

