What are you doing here?

594
00:28:51,590 --> 00:28:54,580
问他。
Ask him.

595
00:28:54,580 --> 00:28:58,800
他逮捕了我因为我试图把我的私人物品带出我的公寓。
He had me arrested for trying to get my personal belongings out Of my apartment.

596
00:28:58,800 --> 00:29:03,400
但他甚至都不想让我给亨利拍照。
But he didn't even want me to take Henry's picture.

597
00:29:03,400 --> 00:29:06,320
这是他唯一拍过的照片。
That's the only picture he ever had taken.

598
00:29:06,320 --> 00:29:08,050
天啊，一点都没变。
Gee, hasn't changed a bit.

599
00:29:08,050 --> 00:29:10,540
我们走吧。
Let's go.

600
00:29:10,540 --> 00:29:11,710
你这个打女人的。
You woman beater.

601
00:29:11,710 --> 00:29:12,670
来吧。
Come on.

602
00:29:12,670 --> 00:29:13,630
叽阿。
Grrr.

603
00:29:13,630 --> 00:29:14,390
来吧。
Come on.

604
