How cozy.

625
00:30:00,090 --> 00:30:00,590
现在,看看。
Now, look.

626
00:30:00,590 --> 00:30:02,280
我是从执照局开始的，宝贝。
I started for the license bureau, baby.

627
00:30:02,280 --> 00:30:06,090
但在下来的路上，我在我以前的宿舍停了下来给你拍了张照片。
But on the way down, I stopped off at my old rooming house To get your photograph.

628
00:30:06,090 --> 00:30:07,860
