I like to look at it when I'm not with you.

629
00:30:07,860 --> 00:30:09,740
房东不让我进去拿。
Well, the landlord wouldn't let me in to get it.

630
00:30:09,740 --> 00:30:11,910
一件事接一件事。
So one thing led to another.

631
00:30:11,910 --> 00:30:13,080
