And where do you think I am?

634
00:30:17,010 --> 00:30:18,150
在牢房里。
In the pokey.

635
00:30:18,150 --> 00:30:20,940
狭小的吗?
The pokey?

636
00:30:20,940 --> 00:30:25,070
呆在那里，保持你原来的样子，美丽。
Stay there, just the way you are, beautiful.

637
00:30:25,070 --> 00:30:28,010
我想记住你微笑的样子。
I want to remember you smiling.

638
00:30:28,010 --> 00:30:28,880
微笑?
Smiling?

639
00:30:28,880 --> 00:30:30,170
看，谁在笑?
Look, who's smiling?

640
00:30:30,170 --> 00:30:34,570
我…你能离开镇子几个小时吗，拜托了?
I'd... Look, would you leave town for a couple of hours, please?

641
00:30:34,570 --> 00:30:36,490
听着，聪明宝贝，你得听我说。
Look, Brainey baby, you got to listen to me.

642
00:30:36,490 --> 00:30:38,400
听你的?
Listen to you?

643
00:30:38,400 --> 00:30:40,030
我的皮大衣听了你的话。
My fur coat listened to you.

644
00:30:40,030 --> 00:30:41,380
我的十块钱听了你的话。
My ten bucks listened to you.

645
00:30:41,380 --> 00:30:42,340
我听了你的话。
I listened to you.

646
00:30:42,340 --> 00:30:44,360
我们都听够了你的话。
We're all fed up listening to you.

647
00:30:44,360 --> 00:30:47,010
嗨，布雷尼，我们开始了!
Hey, Brainey, we're on!

648
00:30:47,010 --> 00:30:48,390
再见，小子。
So long, Kid.

649
00:30:48,390 --> 00:30:49,680
圣诞快乐!
Merry Christmas!

650
00:30:49,680 --> 00:30:55,060
