Well, they like to hear us sing in the pink.

661
00:31:36,010 --> 00:31:39,270
哦，邓克先生，多漂亮的貂皮啊。
Oh, Mr. Dunker, what a beautiful mink.

662
00:31:39,270 --> 00:31:47,070
