I think?

665
00:31:51,060 --> 00:31:54,450
当我们发声时，你的反应令人惊讶。
Your reaction is surprising when we're doing our vocalizing.

666
00:31:54,450 --> 00:31:58,920
是啊，你显然是来看我们唱歌的。
Yes, you obviously came just to see us sing.

667
00:32:02,340 --> 00:32:02,840
好吧,女孩。
OK, girls.

668
00:32:02,840 --> 00:32:03,730
6点回来。
Back at 6 o'clock.

669
00:32:08,850 --> 00:32:09,790
-嗨。-嗨。
- Hi. - Hi.

670
00:32:09,790 --> 00:32:10,370
一些早餐吗?
Some breakfast?

671
00:32:10,370 --> 00:32:11,960
不用了，谢谢。
No, thank you.

672
00:32:11,960 --> 00:32:14,520
查理，我不知道怎么…是的，是的，我知道。
Charlie, I don't know how... Yeah, yeah, I know.

673
00:32:14,520 --> 00:32:17,080
我听说柠檬小子去酒壶了。
I heard about the Lemon Drop Kid going to the jug.

674
00:32:17,080 --> 00:32:18,500
多少钱?
How much?

675
00:32:18,500 --> 00:32:19,000
五十岁。
Fifty.

676
00:32:19,000 --> 00:32:20,010
用我的工资。
Out of my salary.

677
00:32:20,010 --> 00:32:21,430
嗯。
Hm.

678
00:32:21,430 --> 00:32:25,820
你知道吗，为什么每次我追求一个女人，她最后都嫁给了那个鼓手?
You know, why is it every time I go for a dame, She winds up marrying the drummer?

679
00:32:25,820 --> 00:32:31,280
大概在两个金发女郎之前，我在兰花和珍珠上花了很多钱，她勾搭上了一个服务员。
About two blondes ago, I shell a lot Of fortune in orchids and pearls, She hooks up with a waiter.

680
00:32:31,280 --> 00:32:33,100
是啊，一个小胖子。
Huh, yeah, a little fat guy.

681
00:32:33,100 --> 00:32:35,110
我才不要跟什么服务员搞在一起呢。
Well, I'm not getting hooked up with any waiter.

682
00:32:35,110 --> 00:32:39,150
那小子骗了我几次，我不会让他得逞的。
The Kid pulled a couple of fast ones on me, And I'm not letting him get away with it.

683
00:32:39,150 --> 00:32:41,150
他认为他在监狱里很安全。
He thinks he's safe in jail.

684
00:32:41,150 --> 00:32:42,510
嗯。
Hm.

685
00:32:42,510 --> 00:32:43,390
谢谢你,查理。
Thanks, Charlie.

686
00:32:43,390 --> 00:32:46,080
我会还你钱的。
I'll pay you back in money.

687
00:32:46,080 --> 00:32:46,580
是的。
Yeah.

688
00:32:50,050 --> 00:32:51,650
怎么了，圣诞老人?
What's the matter, Santa Claus?

689
00:32:51,650 --> 00:32:53,390
你的驯鹿闯红灯了?
Your reindeer gone through a red light?

690
00:32:53,390 --> 00:32:56,340
圣诞老人今年不是个好孩子。
Santa Claus hasn't been a good boy this year.

691
00:32:56,340 --> 00:32:58,130
他们在你包里发现了什么，圣诞老人?
What did they find in your bag, Santa?

692
00:32:58,130 --> 00:33:00,090
盗窃工具吗?
Burglary tools?

693
00:33:00,090 --> 00:33:02,700
乌合之众。
Riffraff.

694
00:33:02,700 --> 00:33:04,390
有人来看你了，小子。
You got a visitor, Kid.

695
00:33:04,390 --> 00:33:05,910
你的家庭医生。
Your family doctor.

696
00:33:05,910 --> 00:33:07,390
嗯，外科医生山姆。
Well, Sam the Surgeon.

697
00:33:07,390 --> 00:33:09,740
你提前来切圣诞菜了吗?
You come to do your Christmas chopping early?

698
00:33:09,740 --> 00:33:10,390
