00:33:10,390 --> 00:33:13,680
我是来提醒你慕斯·莫兰想要什么圣诞礼物的。
I came to remind you what Moose Moran wants for Christmas.

700
00:33:13,680 --> 00:33:15,930
我记得。
I remember.

701
00:33:15,930 --> 00:33:18,230
你知道吗，小子，躲在监狱里太蠢了。
You know, Kid, jail's a silly place to try to hide.

702
00:33:18,230 --> 00:33:20,260
慕斯的朋友进的比出的多。
Moose has more friends in than out.

703
00:33:20,260 --> 00:33:22,470
山姆，你可以把刀放在樟脑丸里。
Sam, you can put your knife in mothballs.

704
00:33:22,470 --> 00:33:24,300
我有个好主意。
I got an idea that can't miss.

705
00:33:24,300 --> 00:33:26,300
我知道我能弄到一万美元。
I know I can come up with the ten grand.

706
00:33:26,300 --> 00:33:31,250
没关系，因为一些聪明的男孩开始逗慕斯笑了，慕斯不喜欢这样。
That's fine because some of the smart boys Are starting to get Moose to laugh, and Moose don't like it.

707
00:33:31,250 --> 00:33:34,810
我们要做的就是从现在开始借用穆斯的赌场直到圣诞节。
All we have to do is borrow Moose's casino from now Till Christmas.

708
00:33:34,810 --> 00:33:36,720
慕斯不能打开它进行高级赌博。
Moose can't open it for high-class gambling.

709
00:33:36,720 --> 00:33:38,920
你连宾果游戏厅都打不开。
You can't even open it for a bingo parlor.

710
00:33:38,920 --> 00:33:40,700
等等，你在和一个天才说话。
Wait, you're talking to a genius.

711
00:33:40,700 --> 00:33:41,950
你认识Nellie Thursday吗?
You know Nellie Thursday?

712
00:33:41,950 --> 00:33:42,550
她在这里。
She's in here.

713
00:33:42,550 --> 00:33:44,300
她没有地方住。
She's got no place to live.

714
00:33:44,300 --> 00:33:48,530
她想进养老院，但他们不收她，因为她丈夫有前科。
She tried to get into an old folks' home, But they wouldn't take her on account Of her husband's an ex-con.

715
00:33:48,530 --> 00:33:50,120
这是我的想法。
Now, here's the idea.

716
00:33:50,120 --> 00:33:51,910
我借了穆斯的赌场。
I borrow Moose's casino.

717
00:33:51,910 --> 00:33:54,000
我假装这是一家老人院。
I pretend it's an old folks' home.

718
00:33:54,000 --> 00:33:56,360
我把内莉和一堆旧娃娃放在一起。
I stick Nellie in there with a bunch of old dolls.

719
00:33:56,360 --> 00:33:59,260
有他们在里面……这部分有点难。
With them in it... now, this part is kind of tough.

720
00:33:59,260 --> 00:34:04,450
但我想，如果我能做到，我可以说服市政府给我一张为慈善募捐的执照。
But I figure, uh, if I can work it, I can talk the city into giving me A license to collect for charity.

721
00:34:04,450 --> 00:34:08,690
我还想，我可以把百老汇所有的杯子都拿来帮我收集。
I further figure, I can get every mug on Broadway To help me do the collecting.

722
00:34:08,690 --> 00:34:09,880
他们都喜欢内莉。
They all love Nellie.

723
00:34:09,880 --> 00:34:11,590
她真是个漂亮的老娃娃。
She's such a grand old doll.

724
00:34:11,590 --> 00:34:14,510
你想在慕斯的赌场里卖掉一群旧娃娃吗?
You trying to unload a mob of old dolls in Moose's casino?

725
00:34:14,510 --> 00:34:16,130
嘘。
Shh.

726
00:34:16,130 --> 00:34:18,300
只到平安夜。
It's only until Christmas Eve.

727
00:34:18,300 --> 00:34:22,060
到那时，我就能筹到足够的钱还清穆斯。
By then, I'll have collected enough to pay off Moose.

728
00:34:22,060 --> 00:34:25,800
这是我听过的最合法的欺骗。
This is the most legal double cross I've ever heard.

729
00:34:25,800 --> 00:34:28,880
但是圣诞夜过后这些旧娃娃怎么办呢?
But what happens to the old dolls after Christmas Eve?

730
00:34:28,880 --> 00:34:35,620
如果募捐的钱突然丢了而那些旧娃娃也没钱待在赌场了，我能控制得了吗?
Well, can I help it if suddenly the collection money Just happens to get lost and the old dolls Can't afford to stay in the casino?

731
00:34:35,620 --> 00:34:36,500
慕斯会得到他的钱。
Moose will have his dough.

732
00:34:36,500 --> 00:34:38,850
这样我就不会有麻烦了。
And I'll be in the clear, you see.

733
00:34:38,850 --> 00:34:43,800
你要在圣诞节的时候把那些漂亮的小女人都扔到大街上吗?
You're going to dump all those nice little ladies out On the street at Christmastime?

734
00:34:43,800 --> 00:34:46,280
我不会对自己的母亲这么做。
I wouldn't do that to my own mother.

735
00:34:46,280 --> 00:34:48,980
城里任何一家庄家都会给你3比1。
Any bookmaker in town will give you 3-1.

736
00:34:48,980 --> 00:34:50,960
这到底算不算交易?
Is it a deal or not?

737
00:34:50,960 --> 00:34:51,780
听起来很疯狂。
Sounds crazy.

738
00:34:51,780 --> 00:34:53,520
但那不是我的部门。
But that ain't my department.

739
00:34:53,520 --> 00:34:56,990
如果你不给我钱，我就开始手术。
I only to start operating if you don't pay off.

740
00:34:56,990 --> 00:34:57,820
你在哪里实习过?
Where did you intern at?

741
00:34:57,820 --> 00:34:58,740
财务公司?
The finance company?

742
00:34:58,740 --> 00:35:02,770
嘿，山姆，五十美元的罚款有点小问题。
And hey, Sam, there's a little matter of the fifty-dollar fine.

743
00:35:02,770 --> 00:35:06,260
你先垫付，我就欠慕斯一万五。
You advance it, and I owe Moose a round figure of ten thousand and fifty.

744
00:35:06,260 --> 00:35:07,490
不，谢谢，小子。
No, thanks, Kid.

745
00:35:07,490 --> 00:35:09,590
我喜欢你被冷冻起来。
I like having you in the deep freeze.

746
00:35:09,590 --> 00:35:13,620
我们可以在假期前让你暖和起来。
We can thaw you out in time for the holiday season.

747
00:35:13,620 --> 00:35:18,310
再过15天圣诞快乐。
Merry Christmas in just 15 days.

748
00:35:18,310 --> 00:35:19,960
圣诞快乐。
Merry Christmas.

749
00:35:19,960 --> 00:35:20,680
15天。
15 days.

750
00:35:20,680 --> 00:35:21,560
我得离开这里。
I got to get out of here.

751
00:35:21,560 --> 00:35:22,430
我得离开这里!
I got to get out of here!

752
00:35:22,430 --> 00:35:23,370
请放我出去!
Please let me out of here!

753
00:35:23,370 --> 00:35:23,870
嘿!
Hey!

754
00:35:27,280 --> 00:35:29,170
我早就该说"请"了。
I should have said "please" a long time ago.

755
00:35:29,170 --> 00:35:31,170
有一位女士在办公室等你。
There's a lady waiting for you in the office.

756
00:35:31,170 --> 00:35:32,980
她付了你的罚款。
She paid your fine.

757
00:35:34,290 --> 00:35:35,870
再见,圣诞老人!
Goodbye, Santa!

758
00:35:35,870 --> 00:35:38,080
犯!
Delinquents!

759
00:35:38,080 --> 00:35:38,790
这是您的收据。
Here's your receipt.

760
00:35:38,790 --> 00:35:39,520
谢谢你！
Thank you.

761
00:35:39,520 --> 00:35:41,040
Brainey !
Brainey!

762
00:35:41,040 --> 00:35:42,650
我就知道你会来。
I knew you'd come.

763
00:35:42,650 --> 00:35:43,800
无法抗拒，是吗?
Couldn't fight it, eh?

764
00:35:43,800 --> 00:35:46,990
我不知道我会对他们做什么。
I don't know what I'd do to them.

765
00:35:46,990 --> 00:35:48,680
我猜，你在想我的衣服。
Well, I guess, you're wondering about the outfit.

766
00:35:48,680 --> 00:35:50,180
哦，不，运动。
Oh, no, sport.

767
00:35:50,180 --> 00:35:52,210
你总是穿着华丽。
You always were a flashy dresser.

768
00:35:52,210 --> 00:35:54,300
你不知道重获自由是什么感觉。
You don't know how it feels to be free again.

769
00:35:54,300 --> 00:35:56,380
你大概有五分钟的空闲时间。
Well, you're going to be free about five minutes.

770
00:35:56,380 --> 00:35:59,290
我们要去市中心领结婚证。
We're heading downtown for a marriage license.

771
00:35:59,290 --> 00:36:00,050
在一起。
Together.

772
00:36:00,050 --> 00:36:03,020
Brainey，你让我成为世界上最幸福的男人!
Brainey, you're making me the happiest man in the world!

773
00:36:03,020 --> 00:36:07,770
而且再也不会有每周为了区区几块钱跳舞的机会了……当你是我妻子的时候。
And there'd be no more dancing for a few measly dollars A week anymore... not when you're my wife.

774
00:36:07,770 --> 00:36:09,330
我们会让牛津查理给你加薪的。
We'll make Oxford Charlie give you a raise.

775
00:36:09,330 --> 00:36:14,280
哦，我不想工作……想想看，再过几周，我们就是柠檬小子夫妇了。
Oh, I don't want to work... Just think, in a few short weeks, We'll be Mr. And Mrs. Lemon Drop Kid.

776
00:36:17,510 --> 00:36:19,440
短短几周?
A few short weeks?

777
00:36:19,440 --> 00:36:21,010
这次的摊位是什么?
What's the stall this time?

778
00:36:21,010 --> 00:36:22,220
好吧，来吧。
Well, come on.

779
00:36:22,220 --> 00:36:23,460
你会为我感到骄傲的。
You'll be proud of me.

780
00:36:23,460 --> 00:36:25,760
哦。
Oops.

781
00:36:25,760 --> 00:36:27,050
嗨，你好，小子。
Hic, hello, Kid.

782
00:36:27,050 --> 00:36:29,340
又在看电视了?
Been watching television again, huh?

783
00:36:29,340 --> 00:36:30,240
警官，罪名是什么?
What's the charge, Officer?

784
00:36:34,490 --> 00:36:39,290
我跟你说话的时候你能别排练了吗?
Hey, will you stop rehearsing when I'm trying to talk to you?

785
00:36:39,290 --> 00:36:41,460
还记得那次轮到你输的时候你赢了吗?
Remember the time you win when it was your turn to lose?

786
00:36:41,460 --> 00:36:43,040
谁把你藏了三个星期?
Who hide you off for three weeks?

787
00:36:43,040 --> 00:36:44,070
内莉。
Nellie did.

788
00:36:44,070 --> 00:36:46,420
但是，小子，你的个人角度是什么?
But, Kid, what's your personal angle?

789
00:36:46,420 --> 00:36:47,430
闭上嘴，瑞典佬。
Button your lips, Swede.

790
00:36:47,430 --> 00:36:51,110
内莉就像你的母亲。
Nellie is like a mother to you.

791
00:37:00,970 --> 00:37:01,470
叽阿。
Grrr.

792
00:37:04,210 --> 00:37:05,710
柠檬娃娃?
Lemon Drop Kid?

793
00:37:05,710 --> 00:37:08,910
我只是不相信你不关心柠檬滴小孩。
I just don't believe you're not looking out For the Lemon Drop Kid.

794
00:37:08,910 --> 00:37:10,130
但你必须相信。
But you got to believe it.

795
00:37:10,130 --> 00:37:12,270
像Nellie Thursday这样的老太太肯定有好几百个。
There must be hundreds of old ladies like Nellie Thursday.

796
00:37:12,270 --> 00:37:13,700
它们遍布百老汇大街。
They're all around Broadway.

797
00:37:13,700 --> 00:37:19,180
老娃娃们进不了家，因为他们可能在过去卷了一卷，捣碎了一点自制啤酒。
Old dolls who can't get into homes because maybe they Rolled a lusher, pound a little homemade beer in the old days.

798
00:37:19,180 --> 00:37:20,500
甚至是你自己的母亲。
Maybe even your own mother.

799
00:37:20,500 --> 00:37:23,520
他们从来没有责怪过妈妈。
They never hung no rap on Mom.

800
00:37:23,520 --> 00:37:27,680
同花顺托尼，去年你穷困潦倒的时候，谁把你押在了一副有标记的新牌上?
Straight Flush Tony, when you were down and out last year, Who staked you to a new deck of marked cards?

801
00:37:27,680 --> 00:37:28,760
内莉!
Nellie!

802
00:37:28,760 --> 00:37:29,890
好的!
OK!

803
00:37:29,890 --> 00:37:31,680
所以大家都回家好好睡一觉吧。
So everybody go home and get a good night's sleep.

804
00:37:31,680 --> 00:37:33,090
明天中午我们都要起床。
We're all getting up at noon tomorrow.

805
00:37:45,290 --> 00:37:47,320
她来了。
There she is.

806
00:37:47,320 --> 00:37:48,330
记住，一个字也别说。
Remember, not a word.

807
00:37:48,330 --> 00:37:49,420
这是一个惊喜派对。
This is a surprise party.

808
00:37:52,930 --> 00:37:54,360
你好,内莉。
Hello, Nellie.

809
00:37:54,360 --> 00:37:55,280
孩子!
Kid!

810
00:37:55,280 --> 00:37:57,410
哦，阴郁而诚实的哈利。
Oh, Gloomy and Honest Harry.

811
00:37:57,410 --> 00:37:58,040
嘿，内莉。
Hey there, Nellie.

812
00:37:58,040 --> 00:38:00,370
内尔，出来的感觉怎么样?
Ha, Nell, how does it feel to be out?

813
00:38:00,370 --> 00:38:01,240
冷。
Cold.

814
00:38:01,240 --> 00:38:02,410
哦,我的。
Oh, my.

815
00:38:02,410 --> 00:38:04,030
我们有辆好车在等你。
We got a hot car waiting for you.

816
00:38:04,030 --> 00:38:06,750
你们什么时候开始喜欢偷这个了?
Since when have you boys gone in for swiping this?

817
00:38:06,750 --> 00:38:09,030
我们以为你会喜欢兜风的。
Oh, we thought you'd enjoy a little ride.

818
00:38:09,030 --> 00:38:10,180
谢谢，但我要走路。
Thanks, but I'm walking.

819
00:38:10,180 --> 00:38:12,110
在转角处有个小公寓。
There's a two-bit boarding house just around the corner.

820
00:38:12,110 --> 00:38:13,450
好的，我们开车送你去。
Good, we'll drive you there.

821
00:38:13,450 --> 00:38:15,380
你疯了，小子。
Oh, you're crazy, Kid.

822
00:38:15,380 --> 00:38:18,900
等等，谁会开豪华轿车去廉价公寓?
Wait, who pulls up to a cheap boarding house in a limousine?

823
00:38:18,900 --> 00:38:20,280
只有和朋友在一起的旧娃娃。
Only old dolls with friends.

824
00:38:21,000 --> 00:38:21,640
进去。
Get in.

825
00:38:38,060 --> 00:38:42,760
小子，这不是穆斯·莫兰以前的赌场吗?
Why, Kid, isn't this Moose Moran's old gambling casino?

826
00:38:42,760 --> 00:38:45,600
穆斯·莫兰的老什么?
Moose Moran's old what?

827
00:38:45,600 --> 00:38:50,820
“奈莉星期四回家给老娃娃。”
"Nellie Thursday Home for Old Dolls."

828
00:38:50,820 --> 00:38:52,440
这是什么意思，小子?
What does this mean, Kid?

829
00:38:52,440 --> 00:38:55,260
只是长岛的一间小公寓，内莉。
It's just a two-bit boarding house in Long Island, Nellie.

830
00:38:55,260 --> 00:39:01,590
整块地都是后院，冷热相间的矮牵牛花，四面朝南，灰泥浴缸。
Whole field for a backyard, hot and cold running petunias, Southern exposure on all sides, stucco bathtubs.

831
00:39:01,590 --> 00:39:08,460
对了，我差点忘了，有个房间给亨利，里面有个很大的保险箱供他练习。
Oh yeah, I almost forgot, there's A room for Henry with a nice big safe for him to practice on.

832
00:39:08,460 --> 00:39:10,500
嘿,小子。
Hey, Kid.

833
00:39:10,500 --> 00:39:13,420
我和Goomba在公园里发现了这个…解锁。
Me and Goomba found this in the park... unlocked.

834
00:39:13,420 --> 00:39:16,240
我们觉得这样对内莉比较好。
We thought it'd be nice for Nellie.

835
00:39:16,240 --> 00:39:17,050
干得好，Solly。
Oh, good work, Solly.

836
00:39:17,050 --> 00:39:18,210
把它放在草坪上。
Put it out on the lawn.

837
00:39:18,210 --> 00:39:20,240
她在厕所…雕像旁边看起来不错。
She's loo... looking good by the statue.

838
00:39:20,240 --> 00:39:21,870
雕像?
Statue?

839
00:39:21,870 --> 00:39:22,730
听着，我们没有…
Look, we don't have...

840
00:39:25,540 --> 00:39:27,730
将军在中央公园已经坐得够久了。
The general has been sitting in Central Park long enough.

841
00:39:27,730 --> 00:39:29,700
我们觉得他需要换个环境。
We figure he needs a change of scenery.

842
00:39:29,700 --> 00:39:32,230
你把那个将军放回马背上。
You take that general and put him back on his horse.

843
00:39:32,230 --> 00:39:33,100
随你怎么说，小子。
Anything you say, Kid.

844
00:39:36,800 --> 00:39:40,810
我们也觉得将军没了马一定很寂寞。
We, too, figured that general was lonesome without his horse.

845
00:39:40,810 --> 00:39:43,730
他们可能还带了鸽子。
They probably brought the pigeons, too.

846
00:39:43,730 --> 00:39:45,460
嘿，同花顺，帮帮他们?
Hey, Straight Flush, help them, huh?

847
00:39:45,460 --> 00:39:48,590
你还以为我们带你来这里是为了拿免费报纸吗?
You still think we carried you out here To get free newspapers?

848
00:39:48,590 --> 00:39:52,040
你做的…这是一家老人院，不是吗?
You did... it is an old folks' home, isn't it?

849
00:39:52,040 --> 00:39:52,650
当然是。
Sure, it is.

850
00:39:52,650 --> 00:39:53,670
最好的。
The best.

851
00:39:53,670 --> 00:39:57,980
我们会让阳光之家的捕鼠器对我们的溢流感到满意。
We'll make that Sunshine Home rat Trap be satisfied with our overflow.

852
00:39:57,980 --> 00:40:00,320
你做这一切都是为了我?
And you did all this for me?

853
00:40:00,320 --> 00:40:02,870
原来你是百老汇最受欢迎的洋娃娃。
Turns out you're the most popular doll on Broadway.

854
00:40:02,870 --> 00:40:06,350
街上每个骗子都在为你卖命。
Every chiseler on the street is knocking himself out for you.

855
00:40:06,350 --> 00:40:08,360
孩子，我听说过这个地方的时候它还很开放。
Kid, I hear about this place when it was wide open.

856
00:40:08,360 --> 00:40:10,300
但我从不进去。
But I'm never inside.

857
00:40:10,300 --> 00:40:11,850
这是专门给肿胀用的。
It's strictly for swells.

858
00:40:11,850 --> 00:40:12,920
不了。
Not anymore.

859
00:40:12,920 --> 00:40:15,310
百老汇欢迎任何坏掉的旧娃娃。
Any broken down old doll on Broadway is welcome.

860
00:40:21,200 --> 00:40:22,190
惊喜!
Surprise!

861
