A lot of people who love Nellie don't think it's so crazy.

1209
00:58:16,760 --> 00:58:18,760
像你这样聪明的女孩，会放弃工作。
Smart girl, like you, gives up a job.

1210
00:58:18,760 --> 00:58:24,500
街上每一个赌钱的人都在为你的老疯子捐钱。
Every penny ante character on the street Blows his top hustling donations for your old wacky.

1211
00:58:24,500 --> 00:58:25,570
也许古怪。
Maybe wacky.

1212
00:58:25,570 --> 00:58:27,150
但不是小赌注。
But not penny ante.

1213
00:58:27,150 --> 00:58:27,930
这是个大生意。
This is big business.

1214
00:58:27,930 --> 00:58:28,430
哈哈。
Ho-ho.

1215
00:58:28,430 --> 00:58:31,590
为什么，你知道在四天内，我们筹集了将近2000美元吗?
Why, do you know that in four days, we raised almost $2,000?

1216
00:58:31,590 --> 00:58:32,090
好吧。
All right.

1217
00:58:32,090 --> 00:58:37,960
所以你收集…那些穿宽松裤子的圣诞老人筹了两千?
So you collect... those baggy-pants Santas Raised two grand?

1218
00:58:37,960 --> 00:58:39,350
嗯嗯。
Mm-hm.

1219
00:58:39,350 --> 00:58:43,760
你看那小子在这里。
You see the Kid's got it here.

1220
00:58:43,760 --> 00:58:45,250
来，让我来。
Here, let me.

1221
00:58:45,250 --> 00:58:46,530
谢谢你！
Thank you.

1222
00:58:46,530 --> 00:58:54,480
你知道吗，Brainey，当你回来的时候，你的工作就会等着你，这证明我在这里没有。
You know, Brainey, your job will be waiting for you when You come back, which proves that I haven't got it here.

1223
00:59:16,530 --> 00:59:18,030
嘘，嘘，嘘。
Shh, shh, shh.

1224
00:59:35,480 --> 00:59:37,910
头皮屑,嗯?
Dandruff, huh?

1225
00:59:37,910 --> 00:59:41,730
准备好，你们这些野牛小弟，有印第安人来了。
Stand by, you Buffalo nickels, there's some Indians coming.

1226
00:59:42,920 --> 00:59:44,150
合众为一。
E pluribus unum.

1227
00:59:45,350 --> 00:59:45,850
嘘!
Shh!

1228
00:59:45,850 --> 00:59:46,840
安静,令人陶醉。
Quiet, Heady.

1229
00:59:46,840 --> 00:59:47,340
安静。
Quiet.

1230
00:59:52,830 --> 00:59:56,080
给你的菠菜来点苦头。
Giving you your spinach the hard way.

1231
00:59:56,080 --> 00:59:58,740
