Uh, it's you.

1235
01:00:12,700 --> 01:00:13,740
我还以为是小偷呢。
I thought it was a prowler.

1236
01:00:13,740 --> 01:00:14,240
小偷吗?
A prowler?

1237
01:00:16,890 --> 01:00:18,270
有趣的事情。
Funny thing.

1238
01:00:18,270 --> 01:00:22,450
我在给我爱的女孩唱小夜曲，她却认为我是个小偷。
Here I am serenading the girl I love, And she thinks I'm a prowler.

1239
01:00:22,450 --> 01:00:23,940
嗯，我听到了一些声音。
Well, I heard some noise.

1240
01:00:23,940 --> 01:00:25,680
但我不知道它在唱歌。
But I didn't know it was singing.

1241
01:00:25,680 --> 01:00:28,580
我还没唱到副歌呢。
Uh, I didn't get to the chorus yet.

1242
01:00:28,580 --> 01:00:31,690
我只是在这里观察天空，想着你。
I was just out here casing the sky, thinking of you.

1243
01:00:31,690 --> 01:00:35,480
你知道吗，天上的每一颗星星都让我想起你眼中的光芒。
You know, every star up there reminds me Of the light in your eyes.

1244
01:00:35,480 --> 01:00:39,650
一闪一闪，小…哦。
Twinkle, twinkle, little... uh-oh.

1245
01:00:39,650 --> 01:00:42,270
闪烁,闪烁……那是小孩子的东西。
Twinkle, twinkle... That's kid stuff.

1246
01:00:42,270 --> 01:00:43,890
亲爱的，你的尖牙露出来了。
Honey, your fangs are showing.

1247
01:00:59,320 --> 01:01:01,750
如果你得意忘形了，不要克制自己，好吗?
If you get carried away, don't hold yourself back, ha?

1248
01:01:25,110 --> 01:01:27,640
孩子。
Kid.

1249
01:01:27,640 --> 01:01:30,310
亲爱的，永远不要失去我。
Honey, don't ever lose me.

1250
01:01:30,310 --> 01:01:31,530
那会毁了你的。
It would ruin you.

1251
01:01:35,600 --> 01:01:37,980
我们必须马上对柠檬滴小子施压。
We must lean in on the Lemon Drop Kid right away.

1252
01:01:37,980 --> 01:01:42,040
嘿，你不会是想让我们穿上猴子装然后摇起铃铛吧?
Hey, you ain't figuring on us wearing the monkey suits And ringing them little bells?

1253
01:01:42,040 --> 01:01:46,240
听着，如果那小子能在四天内筹到两千，我们能筹到更多。
Look, if the Kid can raise two grand in four days, We can raise lots more than that.

1254
01:01:46,240 --> 01:01:46,850
当然,老板。
Sure, boss.

1255
01:01:46,850 --> 01:01:48,850
孩子们在穆斯·莫兰的赌场里买了一堆旧娃娃。
The kids got a herd of old dolls in Moose Moran's casino.

1256
01:01:48,850 --> 01:01:50,410
他就是这样拿到驾照的。
This is how he gets a license.

1257
01:01:50,410 --> 01:01:51,810
我知道。
I know that.

1258
01:01:51,810 --> 01:01:55,940
我知道执照上写的是给奈莉·星期四之家的。
I know that the license is made out To the Nellie Thursday Home.

1259
01:01:55,940 --> 01:02:02,550
所以我想无论内莉·星期四在哪，那就是内莉·星期四之家，明白吗?
So I figured that wherever Nellie Thursday is, That's the Nellie Thursday Home, you see?

1260
01:02:02,550 --> 01:02:03,820
现在，我们要做的是。
Now, here's what we're going to do.

1261
01:02:10,260 --> 01:02:10,930
看,女孩。
Look, girls.

1262
01:02:10,930 --> 01:02:12,440
先生们要来拜访了。
Gentlemen are coming to call.

1263
01:02:12,440 --> 01:02:13,970
哦，他们给我们带了花!
Oh, and they're bringing us flowers!

1264
01:02:16,560 --> 01:02:17,900
它们必须是有价值的。
They must be valuable.

1265
01:02:17,900 --> 01:02:20,600
他们用枪保护他们。
They're guarding them with a gun.

1266
01:02:20,600 --> 01:02:21,570
把那东西拿开。
Put that thing away.

1267
01:02:21,570 --> 01:02:23,490
你觉得这些旧娃娃会拿杆子吗?
You think these old dolls carry rods?

1268
01:02:23,490 --> 01:02:24,360
你看不出来。
You can't tell.

1269
01:02:24,360 --> 01:02:25,580
那个安妮·奥克利女士呢?
What about that Annie Oakley dame?

1270
01:02:25,580 --> 01:02:28,190
把它收起来，你…好吧。
Put that away, you... All right.

1271
01:02:31,550 --> 01:02:33,990
好了，别忘了。
All right, now, don't forget.

1272
01:02:33,990 --> 01:02:37,100
帽子和"请"和"女士"都要去掉
It's off with the hat and "please" and "ma'am."

1273
01:02:37,100 --> 01:02:38,190
明白了吗?
You got it?

1274
01:02:38,190 --> 01:02:40,410
强尼，你待在这里。
Johnny, you stay here.

1275
01:02:40,410 --> 01:02:41,970
祝福你，善良的先生。
Bless you, kind sir.

1276
01:02:41,970 --> 01:02:42,470
保佑你。
Bless you.

1277
01:02:42,470 --> 01:02:44,480
又一天，又一美元，更少的税。
Another day, another dollar, less taxes.

1278
01:02:44,480 --> 01:02:45,160
谢谢你，女士。
Thank you, ma'am.

1279
01:02:45,160 --> 01:02:47,070
女士。
Ma'am.

1280
01:02:47,070 --> 01:02:48,850
我……圣诞快乐。
Me... merry Christmas.

1281
01:02:48,850 --> 01:02:49,660
圣诞快乐。
Merry Christmas.

1282
01:02:49,660 --> 01:02:51,280
不要被拒之门外。
Don't get shut out.

1283
01:02:51,280 --> 01:02:54,530
Everybod……圣诞快乐。
Everybod... Merry Christmas.

1284
01:02:54,530 --> 01:02:56,400
圣诞快乐。
Merry Christmas.

1285
01:02:56,400 --> 01:02:56,910
哈哈!
Ho-ho!

1286
01:02:57,410 --> 01:03:01,890
哦，对不起，邮件是…对不起，你的钱都撒得到处都是。
Oh, I'm sorry, the post is... sorry, Your money is just spread out all over.

1287
01:03:01,890 --> 01:03:04,210
让我来帮你。
Let me help you with it.

1288
01:03:04,210 --> 01:03:05,410
找钱给你。
You get the change.

1289
01:03:05,410 --> 01:03:06,650
呵呵，呵呵，呵呵。
Ho-ho, ho, ho.

1290
01:03:06,650 --> 01:03:07,880
对不起,先生。
Sorry, sir.

1291
01:03:07,880 --> 01:03:09,470
你在这儿。
There you are.

1292
01:03:09,470 --> 01:03:11,300
先生，往锅里放点东西。
Put something in the pot, sir.

1293
01:03:11,300 --> 01:03:12,630
锅里有东西。
Something in the pot.

1294
01:03:12,630 --> 01:03:13,970
圣诞节的礼物。
Something for Christmas.

1295
01:03:13,970 --> 01:03:14,870
嗬，嗬，嗬。
Ho, ho, ho.

1296
01:03:14,870 --> 01:03:15,680
谢谢你，先生。
Thank you, sir.

1297
01:03:15,680 --> 01:03:16,930
谢谢你！
Thank you.

1298
01:03:16,930 --> 01:03:17,570
Hrrm。
Hrrm.

1299
01:03:17,570 --> 01:03:20,660
圣诞快乐。
Merry Christmas.

1300
01:03:20,660 --> 01:03:23,860
咩……女士，你要为不幸的人做点什么。
Meh... you do, ma'am, something for the less fortunate.

1301
01:03:23,860 --> 01:03:25,840
恐怕我没有零钱。
I'm afraid I haven't any change.

1302
01:03:25,840 --> 01:03:26,920
哦，没关系。
Oh, that's all right.

1303
01:03:26,920 --> 01:03:27,840
我来处理。
I'll handle it.

1304
01:03:32,470 --> 01:03:33,920
我可没想过全部拿走。
Wouldn't think of taking it all.

1305
01:03:33,920 --> 01:03:36,390
圣诞快乐。
Merry Christmas.

1306
01:03:36,390 --> 01:03:40,340
快乐……你好,威利。
Merry... hello, Willie.

1307
01:03:40,340 --> 01:03:41,540
你怎么认识我的?
How do you know me?

1308
01:03:41,540 --> 01:03:43,430
圣诞老人无所不知。
Santa Claus knows everything.

1309
01:03:43,430 --> 01:03:46,890
圣诞老人知道是谁抢劫了圣乔的盒子工厂。
Santa knows who knocked off that box factory at St. Joe.

1310
01:03:46,890 --> 01:03:49,940
圣诞老人甚至知道威利要进去调查银行的情况。
Santa even knows about Willie going In to case the bank setup.

1311
01:03:49,940 --> 01:03:51,270
最好在水壶里放点东西。
Better put something in the kettle.

1312
01:03:51,270 --> 01:03:58,070
怎么，你…如果威利没有在水壶里放点东西，圣诞老人就会停止敲钟，开始为舞蹈者、腾空者和扁平足者吹口哨。
Why, you, uh... If Willie doesn't put something in the kettle, Santa will stop ringing the bell and start Blowing the whistle for Dancer, Prancer, and Flatfoot.

1313
01:03:58,070 --> 01:03:59,800
圣诞快乐。
Merry Christmas.

1314
01:03:59,800 --> 01:04:03,750
呃，呃，呃，呃，呃。
Uh, uh, uh, uh, uh, uh.

1315
01:04:03,750 --> 01:04:05,410
祝新年快乐。
And a happy New Year.

1316
01:04:05,410 --> 01:04:08,330
圣诞快乐。
Merry Christmas.

1317
01:04:08,330 --> 01:04:10,280
嗬，嗬，嗬，嗬。
Ho, ho, ho, ho.

1318
01:04:10,280 --> 01:04:12,230
嗬，嗬，嗬。
Ho, ho, ho.

1319
01:04:12,230 --> 01:04:13,200
嗬，嗬，嗬，嗬，嗬。
Ho, ho, ho, ho, ho.

1320
01:04:22,950 --> 01:04:25,680
在风大的角落辛苦了一天后，没有什么比回家更好的了。
Oh, there's nothing like coming home After a hard day in a windy corner.

1321
01:04:25,680 --> 01:04:27,590
当然，你要和布雷尼共进晚餐。
Sure, you're going to have dinner with Brainey.

1322
01:04:27,590 --> 01:04:30,680
而我，却和一些熟透的海报女郎在一起。
Me, I end up with some of them overripe pin-up girls.

1323
01:04:30,680 --> 01:04:32,440
我本可以去华尔道夫的。
I could have gone to the Waldorf.

1324
01:04:32,440 --> 01:04:32,940
华尔道夫酒店吗?
The Waldorf?

1325
01:04:32,940 --> 01:04:33,880
你怎么敢?
How dare you?

1326
01:04:33,880 --> 01:04:34,650
不要不诚实。
Don't be dishonest.

1327
01:04:34,650 --> 01:04:36,540
这笔钱是内莉·星期四之家的。
This money belongs to the Nellie Thursday Home.

1328
01:04:36,540 --> 01:04:37,270
嗯?
Huh?

1329
01:04:37,270 --> 01:04:39,340
但是标志在哪里呢?
But where is the sign?

1330
01:04:39,340 --> 01:04:41,320
哦，我想是周二洗漱日。
Oh, Tuesday wash day, I guess.

1331
01:04:41,320 --> 01:04:42,800
嘿，门开着。
Hey, the door is open.

1332
01:04:42,800 --> 01:04:43,990
可能晚上出去打马球了。
Probably out playing night polo.

1333
01:04:47,500 --> 01:04:51,880
当你第一次按下按钮时，并没有什么东西从墙上射出来。
First time you pressed the button, And something didn't come shooting out of the wall.

1334
01:04:51,880 --> 01:04:53,220
嘿，那是什么?
Hey, what's that?

1335
01:04:54,390 --> 01:04:57,000
它只是一头牛。
It's just a cow.

1336
01:04:57,000 --> 01:04:59,460
牛在房子里做什么?
What's a cow doing inside a house?

1337
01:04:59,460 --> 01:05:00,840
米尔顿·伯利今晚上演。
Milton Berle is on tonight.

1338
01:05:03,630 --> 01:05:04,970
Brainey吗?
Brainey?

1339
01:05:04,970 --> 01:05:06,760
内莉吗?
Nellie?

1340
01:05:06,760 --> 01:05:07,580
大家都去哪儿了?
Where is everybody?

1341
01:05:07,580 --> 01:05:11,130
是啊，很好，在辛苦为他们攒钱之后。
Yeah, fine welcome after knocking ourselves Out collecting that dough for them.

1342
01:05:11,130 --> 01:05:13,910
哦，他们一定在附近……面团!
Oh, they must be around... the dough!

1343
01:05:22,410 --> 01:05:23,310
它是不见了!
It's gone!

1344
01:05:23,310 --> 01:05:24,470
当然，你拿着它。
Sure, you're holding it.

1345
01:05:24,470 --> 01:05:24,970
不,不。
No, no.

1346
01:05:24,970 --> 01:05:25,820
我指的是收藏。
I mean the collections.

1347
01:05:25,820 --> 01:05:27,500
我把它们藏在这里了。
I have them hidden in here.

1348
01:05:27,500 --> 01:05:28,960
我以为除了我没人知道。
I thought nobody knew about it but me.

1349
01:05:28,960 --> 01:05:35,920
嗯…除了我没有别人，是吗?
Uh... No one but me, huh?

1350
01:05:35,920 --> 01:05:37,370
牛津查理。
An Oxford Charlie.

1351
01:05:37,370 --> 01:05:39,700
还有谁会戴定制的14 AAAA?
Who else wears a custom-made 14 AAAA?

1352
01:05:39,700 --> 01:05:41,720
走吧，我们要去查理在尼亚克的家。
Come on, we're going to Charlie's place in Nyack.

1353
01:05:42,940 --> 01:05:43,440
帮助你自己。
Help yourself.

1354
01:05:43,440 --> 01:05:44,340
冰箱里有牛奶。
There's milk in the icebox.

1355
01:05:44,340 --> 01:05:44,990
进屋去。
Get in the house.

1356
01:05:44,990 --> 01:05:46,020
你想感冒吗?
You want to catch cold?

1357
01:05:58,030 --> 01:06:00,440
你觉得那些小盗窃犯怎么样?
How do you like those petty larceny crooks?

1358
01:06:00,440 --> 01:06:02,530
他们甚至偷了我们的招牌。
They even stole our sign.

1359
01:06:02,530 --> 01:06:04,080
天啊，真是个惊喜派对。
Boy, what a surprise party.

1360
01:06:04,080 --> 01:06:05,350
他们不会料到我们会来。
They'll never expect us.

1361
01:06:10,510 --> 01:06:11,370
请进，先生们。
Come in, gentlemen.

1362
01:06:11,370 --> 01:06:12,290
我在等你。
You were expected.

1363
01:06:12,290 --> 01:06:13,850
是的。
Yeah.

1364
01:06:13,850 --> 01:06:16,660
是的，我知道。
Yeah, I know.

1365
01:06:16,660 --> 01:06:17,630
是的。
Yeah.

1366
01:06:17,630 --> 01:06:20,440
是啊，他来找我要钱的时候我也是这么想的。
Yeah, that's what I figure when he comes to me for the money.

1367
01:06:20,440 --> 01:06:22,500
听着，你能稍等一下吗?
Look, do you mind holding on for a minute?

1368
01:06:22,500 --> 01:06:23,970
不，我不急。
No, I'm in no hurry.

1369
01:06:23,970 --> 01:06:26,510
好的，我稍等。
Yeah, I'll hold on.

1370
01:06:26,510 --> 01:06:28,750
好吧,孩子。
Well, Kid.

1371
01:06:28,750 --> 01:06:29,980
很高兴见到你。
Well, it's nice to see you.

1372
01:06:29,980 --> 01:06:30,650
你要什么?
What'll it be?

1373
01:06:30,650 --> 01:06:31,790
波旁威士忌,苏格兰威士忌吗?
Bourbon, scotch?

1374
01:06:31,790 --> 01:06:33,820
把我们的老女人都倒出来，快点儿。
Just pour out our old ladies and make it snappy.

1375
01:06:33,820 --> 01:06:34,990
啊，别紧张。
Ah, take it easy.

1376
01:06:34,990 --> 01:06:38,650
楼上的女士们在真正的床上非常开心。
The ladies are perfectly happy upstairs in real beds.

1377
01:06:38,650 --> 01:06:40,500
孩子，救救我们。
Kid, Save us.

1378
01:06:40,500 --> 01:06:41,780
我们的囚犯!
We're prisoners!

1379
01:06:41,780 --> 01:06:46,940
菲尼太太想报警，他们打了她的假牙。
Mrs. Feeney tried to call the police, And they hit her false teeth.

1380
