Kid!

1381
01:06:47,880 --> 01:06:48,850
哦，我们去拿东西。
Oh, we'll get our things.

1382
01:06:48,850 --> 01:06:50,000
我们马上下来。
We'll be right down.

1383
01:06:50,000 --> 01:06:51,380
是的，快点。
Yeah, hurry up.

1384
01:06:51,380 --> 01:06:52,720
你知道的，小子。
You know, Kid.

1385
01:06:52,720 --> 01:06:53,910
你真是个天才。
You're a genius.

1386
01:06:53,910 --> 01:06:57,700
我以前还以为你是个小骗子呢。
Just to think that I used to have you Figured for a small-time chiseler.

1387
01:06:57,700 --> 01:07:01,110
而你却把百老汇所有的骗子都变成了马戏团。
And here you are making a circus out of all the con men On Broadway.

1388
01:07:01,110 --> 01:07:03,350
你从哪弄来的那玩意儿?
Where do you get that sucker stuff?

1389
01:07:03,350 --> 01:07:07,320
我们不会因为他在圣诞节坦诚相待就想骗他。
We don't figure a chance to sucker Just because he gets honest at Christmastime.

1390
01:07:07,320 --> 01:07:08,360
不，别转移话题。
No, don't change the subject.

1391
01:07:08,360 --> 01:07:09,880
我们是来找老女人的。
We're here for the old gals.

1392
01:07:09,880 --> 01:07:18,320
我说你们是世界上最大的傻瓜，因为你们在为奈莉·星期四之家募捐，每一分钱都进了那孩子的口袋。
I say you're the biggest suckers In the world because here you are, out collecting money For the Nellie Thursday Home, and every cent goes right Into the Kid's pocket.

1393
01:07:18,320 --> 01:07:19,920
真不敢相信!
I don't believe it!

1394
01:07:19,920 --> 01:07:21,190
我们也不知道。
We don't either.

1395
01:07:21,190 --> 01:07:25,160
我也是，你不能相信牛津·查理这样的人。
Neither do I. You just can't trust A character like Oxford Charlie.

1396
01:07:25,160 --> 01:07:27,480
同花顺，你以前为穆斯·莫兰工作。
Straight Flush, you used to work for Moose Moran.

1397
01:07:27,480 --> 01:07:29,380
我正在佛罗里达和慕斯通话。
I've got Moose on the phone now in Florida.

1398
01:07:29,380 --> 01:07:32,150
问问他为什么那小子要收一万美元。
Ask him why the Kid is collecting ten grand.

1399
01:07:32,150 --> 01:07:34,570
我会问他的。
I'll ask him.

1400
01:07:34,570 --> 01:07:35,720
喂?
Hello?

1401
01:07:35,720 --> 01:07:37,060
你是哪位?
Who is this?

1402
01:07:37,060 --> 01:07:37,920
打错了。
Wrong number.

1403
01:07:37,920 --> 01:07:39,080
来，给我!
Here, give me that!

1404
01:07:39,080 --> 01:07:40,060
别担心，小子。
Don't worry, Kid.

1405
01:07:40,060 --> 01:07:42,970
我们支持你。
We're with you.

1406
01:07:42,970 --> 01:07:43,760
你好,麋鹿。
Hello, Moose.

1407
01:07:43,760 --> 01:07:44,870
这是同花顺。
This is Straight Flush.

1408
01:07:44,870 --> 01:07:50,560
牛津查理想告诉我们"柠檬小子"是个不诚实的人。
Oxford Charlie's trying to tell us The Lemon Drop Kid is something less than on the level.

1409
01:07:50,560 --> 01:07:52,010
是吗?
Yeah?

1410
01:07:52,010 --> 01:07:54,900
嗯。
Hm.

1411
01:07:54,900 --> 01:07:57,990
我想我们是世界上最大的傻瓜了。
I guess we are the biggest suckers in the whole world.

1412
01:07:57,990 --> 01:08:00,730
我以为那小子是我的朋友。
I thought the Kid was my friend.

1413
01:08:00,730 --> 01:08:04,740
我就站在街角，穿着矫揉造作的衣服，摇着我的小铃铛。
And there I am, standing on the corner, wearing a hokey suit, And ringing my little bell.

1414
01:08:04,740 --> 01:08:06,170
嘿，那小子怎么了?
Hey, what happened to the Kid?

1415
01:08:06,170 --> 01:08:07,500
我知道他会怎么样。
I know what's going to happen to him.

1416
01:08:07,500 --> 01:08:08,230
我们去找他。
Let's find him.

1417
01:08:08,230 --> 01:08:09,260
现在，等一下。
Now, wait a minute.

1418
01:08:09,260 --> 01:08:09,920
等一下。
Wait a minute.

1419
01:08:09,920 --> 01:08:11,120
忘了那小子吧。
Forget about the Kid.

1420
01:08:11,120 --> 01:08:12,970
穆斯·莫兰会照顾他的。
Moose Moran will take care of him.

1421
01:08:12,970 --> 01:08:15,260
从现在起，你们为我工作。
From now on, you guys are working for me.

1422
01:08:15,260 --> 01:08:18,230
我们会从这笔生意中赚到每一分钱。
We'll squeeze every dime out of this racket.

1423
01:08:18,230 --> 01:08:20,680
每个人都有很大的分成。
And there'll be a big fat cut for everybody.

1424
01:08:26,580 --> 01:08:29,080
孩子!
Kid!

1425
01:08:29,080 --> 01:08:31,300
孩子，我觉得你是世上最卑微的…现在,Brainey。
Kid, I think that you are the lowest thing... Now, Brainey.

1426
01:08:31,300 --> 01:08:32,440
不要急于下结论。
Don't jump to conclusions.

1427
01:08:32,440 --> 01:08:33,460
我可以解释一切。
I can explain everything.

1428
01:08:33,460 --> 01:08:35,910
从我第一次见到你，你就一直在解释肮脏的把戏。
You've been explaining dirty tricks Since the first time I met you.

1429
01:08:35,910 --> 01:08:36,880
我得筹集一万美元。
Well, I had to raise ten grand.

1430
01:08:36,880 --> 01:08:38,340
你想让我被杀吗?
Did you want me to get killed?

1431
01:08:38,340 --> 01:08:40,390
这是你想到的最好的主意!
That's the best idea you ever had!

1432
01:08:40,390 --> 01:08:44,800
你怎么能这么卑鄙到…我不知道那些老娃娃会这么受欢迎。
How can you be so low as to, uh... I didn't realize the old dolls would take it so big.

1433
01:08:44,800 --> 01:08:47,170
至少，他们还会有回报。
At least, they're going to be around for the payoff.

1434
01:08:47,170 --> 01:08:50,890
在平安夜，慕斯·莫兰会给我打上"付清"的标记
On Christmas Eve, Moose Moran is going To mark me "paid in full."

1435
01:08:50,890 --> 01:08:53,030
那是八天假。
That's eight days off.

1436
01:08:53,030 --> 01:08:54,000
你想让我怎么做?
What do you expect me to do?

1437
01:08:54,000 --> 01:08:56,370
从牛津·查理这样的流氓那里偷钱?
Steal the money back from a hoodlum like Oxford Charlie?

1438
01:08:56,370 --> 01:08:57,230
为什么不呢?
Why not?

1439
01:08:57,230 --> 01:09:02,390
至少百老汇会有人为你流泪。
Then at least, somebody around Broadway Might shed a tear for you.

1440
01:09:02,390 --> 01:09:03,710
我再也不会这么做了。
That's more than I'll ever do again.

1441
01:09:40,060 --> 01:09:41,560
这个戒指多少钱?
How much on this ring?

1442
01:09:42,560 --> 01:09:45,190
你的结婚戒指?
Your wedding ring?

1443
01:09:45,190 --> 01:09:48,220
很抱歉，内莉，我的婚戒太多了。
I'm sorry, Nellie, but I'm loaded up with wedding rings.

1444
01:09:48,220 --> 01:09:49,940
哦,鲁珀特。
Oh, Rupert.

1445
01:09:49,940 --> 01:09:52,130
你得给我点线索。
You got to give me something on it.

1446
01:09:52,130 --> 01:09:59,830
是为今晚的家庭聚会准备的。
It's for, uh, well, tonight's sort of a family reunion.

1447
01:09:59,830 --> 01:10:01,230
好的。
OK.

1448
01:10:01,230 --> 01:10:01,730
把它脱下来。
Take it off.

1449
01:10:01,730 --> 01:10:02,410
我来看看。
I'll have a look.

1450
01:10:08,410 --> 01:10:10,540
很久没戒了。
Haven't had it off a long time.

1451
01:10:17,490 --> 01:10:19,790
你们女人总是匆匆忙忙的。
You women are always in such a rush.

1452
01:10:19,790 --> 01:10:20,790
你想做什么?
What are you trying to do?

1453
01:10:20,790 --> 01:10:21,690
抢劫她的珠宝?
Heist her jewelry?

1454
01:10:29,970 --> 01:10:32,590
孩子，我的麻烦够多了。
Kid, I got enough trouble.

1455
01:10:32,590 --> 01:10:34,630
你现在想从我这里得到什么?
What do you want from me now?

1456
01:10:34,630 --> 01:10:38,840
听着，内莉，一群好人为你筹了很多钱。
Look, Nellie, a bunch of swell guys collected a lot of money For you.

1457
01:10:38,840 --> 01:10:44,240
我不会让一个骗子，一个骗子，和一个面包屑把事情搞糟。
I'm not going to let a cheat, chiseler, And a crumb gum up the worse.

1458
01:10:44,240 --> 01:10:46,680
你是说牛津查理吧。
You mean Oxford Charlie.

1459
01:10:46,680 --> 01:10:48,470
谁?
Who?

1460
01:10:48,470 --> 01:10:49,930
是的。
Yeah.

1461
01:10:49,930 --> 01:10:51,250
你是怎么从他家逃出来的?
Say, how did you get out of his place?

1462
01:10:51,250 --> 01:10:52,840
其他的娃娃和布雷尼呢?
Where are the other dolls and Brainey?

1463
01:10:52,840 --> 01:10:54,210
还在尼亚克。
Still in Nyack.

1464
01:10:54,210 --> 01:10:56,740
我等待机会，然后偷偷溜了出去。
I waited for my chance, and then I sneaked out.

1465
01:10:56,740 --> 01:10:58,860
好吧，如果你能溜出去，我也能溜进去。
Yeah, well, if you can sneak out, I can sneak in.

1466
01:10:58,860 --> 01:11:01,930
我要去拿那些属于你和其他旧娃娃的钱。
I'm going to get that money that belongs To you and the other old dolls.

1467
01:11:01,930 --> 01:11:02,960
孩子，别试。
Kid, don't try it.

1468
01:11:02,960 --> 01:11:04,560
你不会成功的。
You'll never make it.

1469
01:11:04,560 --> 01:11:06,830
查理那儿到处都是警卫。
Why, Charlie's got guards all over there.

1470
01:11:06,830 --> 01:11:08,180
和他……看，看，内莉。
And he's... Look, look, Nellie.

1471
01:11:08,180 --> 01:11:08,850
我有一个角度。
I've got an angle.

1472
01:11:08,850 --> 01:11:10,660
现在，再听我说一次。
Now, listen to me, just once more.

1473
01:11:10,660 --> 01:11:12,170
我要你把所有男孩都召集起来。
I want you to round up all the boys.

1474
01:11:12,170 --> 01:11:13,370
带他们去法院。
Take them to the courthouse.

1475
01:11:13,370 --> 01:11:14,210
联系一下法官。
Get a hold of the judge.

1476
01:11:14,210 --> 01:11:14,870
和…
And...

1477
01:13:40,080 --> 01:13:41,080
一步……别挡我的路!
Step... get out of my way!

1478
01:13:41,080 --> 01:13:42,070
你好,首席。
Hello, Chief.

1479
01:14:25,700 --> 01:14:26,920
一共95美分。
That'll be 95 cents.

1480
01:14:26,920 --> 01:14:28,880
哦,是的。
Oh, yeah.

1481
01:14:35,240 --> 01:14:38,380
95美分和1美元给你自己。
95 cents and a dollar for yourself.

1482
01:14:38,380 --> 01:14:39,150
哦，不，妈妈。
Oh, no, mother.

1483
01:14:39,150 --> 01:14:40,730
你不用给我小费。
You don't have to tip me.

1484
01:14:40,730 --> 01:14:41,770
真的吗?
Really?

1485
01:14:41,770 --> 01:14:43,440
嗯,在这里。
Well, here.

1486
01:14:43,440 --> 01:14:44,260
来支雪茄。
Have a cigar.

1487
01:14:55,600 --> 01:14:58,400
梦想不需要花费一分钱。
It doesn't cost a dime to dream.

1488
01:14:58,400 --> 01:15:00,890
我们会在墙上挂满美钞。
We'll line our walls with dollar bills.

1489
01:15:15,360 --> 01:15:16,360
是吗?
Yeah?

1490
01:15:16,360 --> 01:15:19,460
我是个没饭吃的可怜老太太，好心的先生。
I'm a poor old lady who haven't got to eat, Kind sir.

1491
01:15:19,460 --> 01:15:22,700
我听说这是一个老太太的家…当然了。
And I heard this was an old lady's home... Sure it is.

1492
01:15:22,700 --> 01:15:24,850
但我们的耳朵都在老娃娃的嘴里了。
But we're up to our ears in old dolls' mouths.

1493
01:15:24,850 --> 01:15:27,570
但我无处可去。
Oh, but I have no place to go.

1494
01:15:27,570 --> 01:15:31,660
我这辈子都得省吃俭用来养孩子。
All my life, I've had to scrimp and save To support my children.

1495
01:15:31,660 --> 01:15:37,220
我日复一日地在火炉上做饭，一直缝到眼睛发麻。
I've sewed till my eyes burned, cooked over a hot stove day After day.

1496
01:15:37,220 --> 01:15:39,840
我甚至还得把地板拿去洗。
I even have to take in floors to wash.

1497
01:15:39,840 --> 01:15:40,870
对不起，老娃娃。
Sorry, old doll.

1498
01:15:40,870 --> 01:15:41,520
不行。
No dice.

1499
01:15:41,520 --> 01:15:43,020
哦，拜托，先生。
Oh, please, sir.

1500
01:15:43,020 --> 01:15:47,070
如果你把我拒之门外，我将无处可去，只能去找当局。
If you turn me away, I'll have no place To go except to the authorities.

1501
01:15:47,070 --> 01:15:48,630
呃，等等，女士。
Eh, uh, hold it, ma'am.

1502
01:15:48,630 --> 01:15:49,250
嗯，请进。
Eh, come right in.

1503
01:15:49,250 --> 01:15:50,300
我会跟老板说的。
I'll talk to the boss.

1504
01:15:50,300 --> 01:15:54,520
既然你是个没饭吃的可怜老太太，也许他会改变我的想法。
Seeing as you're a poor old lady who hasn't got to eat, Maybe he'll change my mind.

1505
01:15:54,520 --> 01:15:56,160
在这儿等着，我为你美言几句。
Wait here while I put in a kind word for you.

1506
01:15:56,160 --> 01:15:56,760
嗯嗯。
Mm-hm.

1507
01:16:02,040 --> 01:16:02,540
嗯嗯。
Mm-hm.

1508
01:16:09,670 --> 01:16:12,090
那是个老太太?
That's an old lady?

1509
01:16:12,090 --> 01:16:14,090
头儿，她又想从窗户逃出去了。
Boss, she was trying to get out the window again.

1510
01:16:14,090 --> 01:16:14,820
内莉的消失了。
Nellie's disappeared.

1511
01:16:14,820 --> 01:16:16,170
必须有人找到她。
And somebody's got to find her.

1512
01:16:16,170 --> 01:16:21,000
布雷尼，我警告过你要守规矩，否则我就要让孩子们…我会想尽一切办法离开这里。
Brainey, I warned you to stay in line, Or I'm going to have the boys... I'll get out of here any way I can.

1513
01:16:21,000 --> 01:16:21,860
那好吧。
All right then.

1514
01:16:21,860 --> 01:16:23,440
带她回房间去。
Take her back to her room.

1515
01:16:23,440 --> 01:16:26,190
跟着她，直到把他们都搬走为止。
And stick with her until it's time to move them all out.

1516
01:16:26,190 --> 01:16:28,720
外面那个新的旧娃娃呢?
And what about the new old doll outside?

1517
01:16:28,720 --> 01:16:32,050
好吧，再喝几小时也无妨。
Well, one more for a couple of hours won't hurt anything.

1518
01:16:32,050 --> 01:16:33,610
而且，我们不能让她去报警。
Besides, we can't have her going to the police.

1519
01:16:33,610 --> 01:16:34,490
好吧，带她进来。
All right, show her in.

1520
01:16:47,440 --> 01:16:49,780
这就是她，老板。
This is her, boss.

1521
01:16:49,780 --> 01:16:51,030
太太比斯利。
Mrs. Beasley.

1522
01:16:51,030 --> 01:16:53,150
赫伯特·比斯利夫人。
Mrs. Herbert Beasley.

1523
01:16:53,150 --> 01:16:55,590
欢迎来到我们家，比斯利夫人。
Well, welcome to our home, Mrs. Beasley.

1524
01:16:55,590 --> 01:16:58,590
你知道吗，你正好赶上搬到我们的新地方。
You know, you're just in time to move to our new location.

1525
01:16:58,590 --> 01:17:02,310
你看，其他女孩会一直待在这房子里直到圣诞节。
See, the other girls are just going to stay in this house Until Christmastime.

1526
01:17:02,310 --> 01:17:04,040
然后他们搬到一个真正的豪宅。
Then they move to a real mansion.

1527
01:17:04,040 --> 01:17:05,250
大得像赌场。
Big as a casino.

1528
01:17:05,250 --> 01:17:07,550
哦，听起来太棒了!
Oh, that sounds wonderful!

1529
01:17:07,550 --> 01:17:09,400
这意味着你接受我为客人了吗?
Does it mean that you accept me as a guest?

1530
01:17:09,400 --> 01:17:10,090
嗯嗯。
Mm-hm.

1531
01:17:10,090 --> 01:17:13,410
我高兴得都想哭了。
Oh, I'm so happy, I could cry.

1532
01:17:13,410 --> 01:17:14,210
好吧，好吧。
All right, all right.

1533
01:17:14,210 --> 01:17:14,710
这是……
That's...

1534
01:17:18,620 --> 01:17:22,200
-我的药。-我的药。
- My medicine. - My medicine.

1535
01:17:22,200 --> 01:17:23,880
哦。
Oh.

1536
01:17:23,880 --> 01:17:27,440
马克西，把她和其他漂亮的老太太带进去，好吗?
Hey, Maxie, take her in with the other nice old ladies, Will you?

1537
01:17:27,440 --> 01:17:29,430
我永远不会忘记你的。
Oh, I'll never forget you for this.

1538
01:17:29,430 --> 01:17:30,480
你是个好人。
You're a good man.

1539
01:17:30,480 --> 01:17:31,880
你是个很好的人。
You're a very good man.

1540
01:17:31,880 --> 01:17:32,560
啊，算了吧。
Ah, forget it.

1541
01:17:32,560 --> 01:17:33,670
谢谢你！
Thank you.

1542
01:17:33,670 --> 01:17:34,700
嘿，好老太太!
Hey, nice old lady!

1543
01:17:34,700 --> 01:17:36,300
你拿错包了。
You've got the wrong bag.

1544
01:17:36,300 --> 01:17:37,230
哦，我的天哪!
Oh, my goodness!

1545
01:17:37,230 --> 01:17:38,970
我确实犯了个错误。
I did make a mistake.

1546
01:17:38,970 --> 01:17:40,690
笨拙的我。
Clumsy me.

1547
01:17:40,690 --> 01:17:41,660
很重，不是吗?
Heavy, isn't it?

1548
01:17:41,660 --> 01:17:42,640
你在用什么编织?
What are you knitting with?

1549
01:17:42,640 --> 01:17:43,260
钢丝绒?
Steel wool?

1550
01:17:43,260 --> 01:17:44,250
嗯。
Hm.

1551
01:17:44,250 --> 01:17:54,360
如果我能买得起新眼镜，我就…梦想不需要花费一分钱……
If I could only afford some new glasses, I... It doesn't cost a dime to dream...

1552
01:17:58,610 --> 01:18:01,020
女士们，这位是俱乐部的新成员，比斯利夫人。
Ladies, meet a new member of the club, Mrs. Beasley.

1553
01:18:01,020 --> 01:18:01,990
你好，比斯利夫人。
How do you do, Mrs. Beasley?

1554
01:18:01,990 --> 01:18:05,800
我知道和你们这些好人在一起我会很快乐的。
I know I'm going to be Happy with all you nice people.

1555
01:18:05,800 --> 01:18:07,320
很高兴你能来。
So nice to have you.

1556
01:18:07,320 --> 01:18:10,030
嗯，可怜的孩子。
Hm, you poor dear.

1557
01:18:10,030 --> 01:18:11,030
坐在这里。
Sit here.

1558
01:18:11,030 --> 01:18:12,320
哦，谢谢。
Oh, thank you.

1559
01:18:24,060 --> 01:18:24,560
嗯嗯。
Mm-hm.

1560
01:18:28,910 --> 01:18:30,420
女士们，这不是一个可爱的家吗?
Isn't this a lovely home, ladies?

1561
01:18:30,420 --> 01:18:32,510
我们不想让你失望，比斯利夫人。
We hate to disillusion you, Mrs. Beasley.

1562
01:18:32,510 --> 01:18:34,500
那是个又大又硬的老监狱。
It's a great, big, hard old jail.

1563
01:18:34,500 --> 01:18:36,070
监狱吗?
Jail?

1564
01:18:36,070 --> 01:18:37,440
亲爱的我!
Dear me!

1565
01:18:37,440 --> 01:18:40,840
但是典狱长……呃，那个主管看起来是个不错的人。
But the warden... uh, the superintendent Seem like such a nice one.

1566
01:18:40,840 --> 01:18:42,270
那不是主管。
That's not the superintendent.

1567
01:18:42,270 --> 01:18:44,400
他是牛津查理，那个敲诈犯。
He's Oxford Charlie, the racketeer.

1568
01:18:44,400 --> 01:18:45,330
恐怖!
Horrors!

1569
01:18:45,330 --> 01:18:47,650
他跟柠檬小子一样是个大流氓。
He's as big a hoodlum as The Lemon Drop Kid.

1570
01:18:50,290 --> 01:18:52,190
嗯。
Hm.

1571
01:18:52,190 --> 01:18:55,540
亲爱的，你在忙什么呢?
What are you working on, dear?

1572
01:18:58,850 --> 01:19:01,060
哦，哈哈。
Oh, ha, ha.

1573
01:19:01,060 --> 01:19:02,760
在Gen之后。
Uh, after Gen.

1574
01:19:02,760 --> 01:19:07,610
卡斯特被杀了，比斯利先生坚持要我一直带着他的手枪。
Custer was massacred, Mr. Beasley Insisted I carry his pistol at all times.

1575
01:19:07,610 --> 01:19:08,790
印度人，你知道的。
Indians, you know.

1576
01:19:08,790 --> 01:19:10,850
嗯。
Hm.

1577
01:19:10,850 --> 01:19:12,450
讨厌的红人队。
Pesky redskins.

1578
01:19:12,450 --> 01:19:14,780
你到底在织什么?
What in the world are you knitting?

1579
01:19:14,780 --> 01:19:16,150
拖把。
Uh, a mop.

1580
01:19:19,800 --> 01:19:21,220
到处都找不到。
Hard to get them anywhere.

1581
01:19:21,220 --> 01:19:24,000
它们和我的阿盖尔磨砂桶很搭。
And they go so well with my Argyle scrub bucket.

1582
01:19:29,330 --> 01:19:34,610
你不觉得大一点的腰带，在我们这个年纪会更明智吗?
Eh, don't you think a larger sized girdle would, uh, Be much more sensible at our age?

1583
01:19:34,610 --> 01:19:35,880
我把它拿得很小。
I take it small.

1584
01:19:35,880 --> 01:19:37,490
总是有。
Always have.

1585
01:19:37,490 --> 01:19:41,010
亲爱的比斯利先生，他为我沙漏般的身材感到骄傲。
Dear Mr. Beasley, he was so proud of my hourglass figure.

1586
01:19:41,010 --> 01:19:43,350
亲爱的，你的身材还是那么沙漏。
You still have your hourglass figure, dear.

1587
01:19:43,350 --> 01:19:44,140
谢谢你！
Thank you.

1588
01:19:44,140 --> 01:19:46,370
但是大部分沙子都沉到了海底。
But most of the sand has gone to the bottom.

1589
01:19:46,370 --> 01:19:47,790
是的。
Yes.

1590
01:19:51,590 --> 01:19:52,720
好了，老女孩们。
There we go, old girls.

1591
01:19:52,720 --> 01:19:53,520
大家准备好。
Everybody get ready.

1592
01:19:53,520 --> 01:19:54,140
我们要搬出去。
We're moving out.

1593
01:19:54,140 --> 01:19:57,360
老花店又要送货了。
The Old Flower Shoppe is going to make another delivery.

1594
01:19:57,360 --> 01:19:58,620
来吧。
Come on.

1595
01:19:58,620 --> 01:19:59,290
这太离谱了!
This is outrageous!

1596
01:20:00,720 --> 01:20:02,390
那是一次短暂的拜访，不是吗?
That was a short visit, wasn't it?

1597
01:20:02,390 --> 01:20:02,960
我的纱!
My yarn!

1598
01:20:02,960 --> 01:20:03,630
哦,是的。
Oh, yes.

1599
01:20:03,630 --> 01:20:05,110
嗯嗯。
Mm-hm.

1600
01:20:05,110 --> 01:20:06,590
哦!
Oh!

1601
01:20:11,520 --> 01:20:13,900
来吧，亲爱的。
Come along, dear.

1602
01:20:13,900 --> 01:20:14,800
来了,来了。
Coming, coming.

1603
01:20:17,540 --> 01:20:18,040
我的外套。
My coat.

1604
01:20:18,040 --> 01:20:18,950
我的外套!
My coat!

1605
01:20:18,950 --> 01:20:20,250
他们在外面的卡车里。
They're out in the truck.

1606
01:20:20,250 --> 01:20:21,340
你的狗!
You dog!

1607
01:20:21,340 --> 01:20:22,460
来吧，老娃娃!
Come on, old doll!

1608
01:20:22,460 --> 01:20:23,460
来了,来了。
Coming, coming.

1609
01:20:46,960 --> 01:20:48,110
你知道你在干什么吗?
What do you think you're doing?

1610
01:20:48,110 --> 01:20:50,580
我以为你们这些漂亮的旧娃娃都没了。
I thought all you nice old dolls had left.

1611
01:20:50,580 --> 01:20:52,050
我不是一个可爱的老娃娃。
I'm not a nice old doll.

1612
01:20:52,050 --> 01:20:53,890
我不会走的。
And I'm not leaving.

1613
01:20:53,890 --> 01:20:55,380
我没有枪!
And I haven't got a gun!

1614
01:20:55,380 --> 01:20:56,370
柠檬滴小孩!
The Lemon Drop Kid!

1615
01:20:56,370 --> 01:20:57,370
小心!
Watch out!

1616
01:20:57,370 --> 01:21:00,850
哦,不!
Oh, no!

1617
01:21:00,850 --> 01:21:01,350
关税…
Impost...

1618
01:21:22,270 --> 01:21:23,260
噢!
Ow!

1619
01:21:23,260 --> 01:21:23,760
喂!
Ho!

1620
01:21:23,760 --> 01:21:24,760
上帝!
God!

1621
01:21:24,760 --> 01:21:25,260
啊!
Ugh!

1622
01:21:25,260 --> 01:21:25,760
嘿!
Hey!

1623
01:21:25,760 --> 01:21:27,250
我的脚!
My foot!

1624
01:21:27,250 --> 01:21:30,240
在哪里…哦!
Where is the... oh!

1625
01:21:31,230 --> 01:21:32,230
不!
No!

1626
01:21:42,690 --> 01:21:45,930
哦，呃，打扰一下，老板。
Oh, uh, excuse me, boss.

1627
01:21:45,930 --> 01:21:47,130
停止它!
Stop it!

1628
01:21:47,130 --> 01:21:48,120
你弄疼我了!放开!
You're hurting me! Let go!

1629
01:21:48,120 --> 01:21:49,110
你弄皱我的裙子了!
You're wrinkling my dress!

1630
01:21:49,110 --> 01:21:49,610
你疯了!
You're mad!

1631
01:21:49,610 --> 01:21:51,590
他弄得我屁股都快断了!
He's busting my hip!

1632
01:21:51,590 --> 01:21:53,080
救救我!
Someone save me!

1633
01:21:53,080 --> 01:21:55,560
救我!
Save me!

1634
01:21:55,560 --> 01:21:58,040
给我!
Give me that!

1635
01:22:20,850 --> 01:22:21,350
啊!
Ugh!

1636
01:22:24,900 --> 01:22:26,480
是你叫我的，老大?
You called me, boss?

1637
01:22:26,480 --> 01:22:27,980
年轻人，给我让开!
Young man, get out of my way!

1638
01:22:27,980 --> 01:22:30,450
她是柠檬娃娃!
She's the Lemon Drop Kid!

1639
01:22:30,450 --> 01:22:31,440
诱饵!
Stool pigeon!

1640
01:22:31,440 --> 01:22:32,290
为什么,你!
Why, you!

1641
01:22:32,290 --> 01:22:32,920
不!
No!

1642
01:22:32,920 --> 01:22:33,670
不!
No!

1643
01:22:33,670 --> 01:22:35,950
你用这个不会伤害任何女士的!
You wouldn't hurt no lady with that!

1644
01:22:39,910 --> 01:22:40,920
他做到了。
He did.

1645
01:22:40,920 --> 01:22:41,880
得到她!
Get her!

1646
01:22:41,880 --> 01:22:43,360
他拿了我的钱!
He's got my money!

1647
01:22:48,300 --> 01:22:49,290
那是柠檬娃娃。
That's the Lemon Drop Kid.

1648
01:22:49,290 --> 01:22:50,280
我们去抓他!
Let's get him!

1649
01:22:56,360 --> 01:22:57,690
往那边走!
Go around that way!

1650
01:22:57,690 --> 01:22:59,170
他不能穿着这些裙子跑!
He can't run in those skirts!

1651
01:23:03,620 --> 01:23:04,610
女士，我是迪克·丹尼尔斯。
Ma'am, Dick Daniels.

1652
01:23:04,610 --> 01:23:05,620
人巡逻。
People Patrol.

1653
01:23:05,620 --> 01:23:06,310
我能为您效劳吗?
May I be of service?

1654
01:23:06,310 --> 01:23:07,240
好的，谢谢你。
Well, thank you.

1655
01:23:07,240 --> 01:23:09,220
哈里特·比斯利，驿马快信。
Harriet Beasley, Pony Express.

1656
01:23:09,220 --> 01:23:10,700
邮件一定能到达。
The mail must go through.

1657
01:23:10,700 --> 01:23:11,690
谢谢你！
Thank you!

1658
01:23:20,580 --> 01:23:22,060
哦!
Oops!

1659
01:23:22,060 --> 01:23:23,050
小心!
Watch out!

1660
01:23:27,990 --> 01:23:28,490
来吧。
Come on.

1661
01:23:28,490 --> 01:23:29,470
把它弄出去。
Get it out of here.

1662
01:23:29,470 --> 01:23:30,460
备份。
Back it up.

1663
01:23:35,400 --> 01:23:35,900
哇!
Whoa!

1664
01:23:41,820 --> 01:23:43,310
的借口!
Excuse!

1665
01:23:43,310 --> 01:23:44,790
不好意思。
Oops, pardon me.

1666
01:23:49,700 --> 01:23:53,180
对不起，我的房间着火了。
Pardon me, my room's on fire.

1667
01:23:54,670 --> 01:23:55,170
哎呀!
Whoops!

1668
01:24:19,390 --> 01:24:20,830
你没事吧，妈妈?
You all right, mother?

1669
01:24:20,830 --> 01:24:21,930
妈妈吗?
Mother?

1670
01:24:21,930 --> 01:24:22,980
我还没结婚呢。
I'm not even married.

1671
01:24:33,810 --> 01:24:34,960
你看到我看到的了吗?
Did you see what I saw?

1672
01:24:34,960 --> 01:24:37,390
是的，我看到她了。
Yeah, I saw her.

1673
01:24:37,390 --> 01:24:38,410
你看见一位老太太了吗?
Did you see an old lady?

1674
01:24:38,410 --> 01:24:40,170
是的，她在里面，警官。
Yes, she's in there, Officer.

1675
01:24:40,170 --> 01:24:40,940
是吗?
Yeah?

1676
01:24:40,940 --> 01:24:42,270
她活不了多久了。
Not for long, she ain't.

1677
01:24:46,130 --> 01:24:47,260
你看到里面有个老太太吗?
Did you see an old lady in there?

1678
01:24:47,260 --> 01:24:47,860
一个老太太?
An old lady?

1679
01:24:47,860 --> 01:24:48,690
啊，哈哈，很有趣。
Ah, ha-ha, very funny.

1680
01:24:48,690 --> 01:24:49,480
我听到了。
I heard it.

1681
01:24:49,480 --> 01:24:50,650
我看见的那个老太太是谁?
Who was that old lady I saw?

1682
01:24:50,650 --> 01:24:51,520
哈哈，很好。
Ha-ha, very good.

1683
01:24:51,520 --> 01:24:52,830
我是毛巾公司的。
I'm with the towel company.

1684
01:24:52,830 --> 01:24:53,330
Hrrm。
Hrrm.

1685
01:25:02,260 --> 01:25:05,370
我在佛罗里达听到的关于旧娃娃之家的事是怎么回事?
What's this I hear in Florida about an old dolls' home?

1686
01:25:05,370 --> 01:25:06,600
这是那小子的主意。
It was the Kid's idea.

1687
01:25:06,600 --> 01:25:09,260
我说他疯了，但他就是这么筹到钱的。
I told him he was crazy, but that's How he figured to raise the money.

1688
01:25:09,260 --> 01:25:12,000
我不想让旧娃娃或其他任何人在这里鬼混。
I don't want old dolls or anybody else Fooling around here.

1689
01:25:12,000 --> 01:25:15,820
纽约警察会因为我又开了这家店而把我绞死的。
The New York cops would love to hang one On me for opening this place again.

1690
01:25:15,820 --> 01:25:19,640
我们抓住那小子，然后把他关起来。
We collect on the Kid, and then lock it up tight.

1691
01:25:19,640 --> 01:25:21,650
嗨,孩子。
Hi, Kid.

1692
01:25:21,650 --> 01:25:23,630
山姆告诉我你筹到了一万美元。
Sam tells me you raised the ten grand.

1693
01:25:23,630 --> 01:25:24,400
这很好。
That's good.

1694
01:25:24,400 --> 01:25:25,020
是的。
Yeah.

1695
01:25:25,020 --> 01:25:26,900
我都帮你算好了。
I got it all counted out for you.

1696
01:25:26,900 --> 01:25:29,100
给你，一万英镑。
Here you are, ten thousand even.

1697
01:25:29,100 --> 01:25:32,330
快到圣诞节了，再过十五分钟就到了。
Say, it's almost Christmas, just fifteen minutes more.

1698
01:25:32,330 --> 01:25:36,480
难道你不愿意给我五千块来展示你的圣诞精神吗?
Wouldn't you like to settle for five thousand just To show your Christmas spirit, huh?

1699
01:25:36,480 --> 01:25:40,170
丫……7500年?
Would ya... 75 hundred?

1700
01:25:40,170 --> 01:25:41,060
没有精神，是吧?
No spirit, huh?

1701
01:25:41,060 --> 01:25:42,060
你可以忘了我的礼物。
You can forget my presents.

1702
01:25:42,060 --> 01:25:45,260
你不必…好吧，一万偶数。
You don't have to... OK, ten thousand even.

1703
01:25:45,260 --> 01:25:46,370
全额支付。
Paid in full.

1704
01:25:48,470 --> 01:25:49,980
穆斯，你好。
Well, Moose, hello.

1705
01:25:49,980 --> 01:25:50,840
你什么时候进城的?
When did you hit town?

1706
01:25:50,840 --> 01:25:51,820
刚到，查理。
Just arrived, Charlie.

1707
01:25:51,820 --> 01:25:53,410
有些收集工作要做。
Had some collecting to do.

1708
01:25:53,410 --> 01:25:54,500
你这个叛徒。
Oh, you rat.

1709
01:25:54,500 --> 01:25:55,600
那是我的钱袋。
That's my money bag.

1710
01:25:55,600 --> 01:25:56,850
我的一万六千呢?
Where's my 16 grand?

1711
01:25:56,850 --> 01:25:58,740
哦，好吧，在这儿。
Oh, well, here it is.

1712
01:25:58,740 --> 01:26:00,150
我只是借来的。
I just borrowed it.

1713
01:26:00,150 --> 01:26:00,730
你在这儿。
There you are.

1714
01:26:00,730 --> 01:26:01,560
现在，你得到了回报。
Now, you're paid off.

1715
01:26:01,560 --> 01:26:02,240
你得到了回报。
And you're paid off.

1716
01:26:02,240 --> 01:26:03,220
每个人都很开心。
And everybody's happy.

1717
01:26:03,220 --> 01:26:05,250
让我们握握手，祝彼此圣诞快乐，好吗?
Let's shake hands and wish each other a Merry Christmas, huh?

1718
01:26:05,250 --> 01:26:06,060
等一下。
Just a minute.

1719
01:26:06,060 --> 01:26:08,280
你欠我一万块钱。
You owe me ten grand.

1720
01:26:08,280 --> 01:26:09,250
哦，是的，你就是那个人。
Oh, yeah, you're the one.

1721
01:26:09,250 --> 01:26:10,000
你在这儿。
There you are.

1722
01:26:10,000 --> 01:26:10,990
你不需要算出来。
You don't have to work it out.

1723
01:26:10,990 --> 01:26:11,690
我做了我该做的。
I've done my share.

1724
01:26:11,690 --> 01:26:13,560
你为什么要凿……山姆!
Why you chiseling... Sam!

1725
01:26:24,430 --> 01:26:26,410
我们不能在这里赌博!
We can't have gambling here!

1726
01:26:26,410 --> 01:26:27,900
萨姆，去拿开关!
Get that switch, Sam!

1727
01:26:27,900 --> 01:26:29,390
去拿开关!
Get the switch!

1728
01:26:29,390 --> 01:26:31,370
呃，这样换一下怎么样?
Ho, how's that for a switch?

1729
01:26:31,370 --> 01:26:31,870
走吧!
Go!

1730
01:26:31,870 --> 01:26:32,860
让我们活得轻松一点吧，伙计们。
Let's live a little, folks.

1731
01:26:32,860 --> 01:26:33,850
萨利，他们胆子更大。
Solly, they're bolder.

1732
01:26:33,850 --> 01:26:34,840
-带他过去。-让我揍他!
- Get him there. - Let me just beat him!

1733
01:26:34,840 --> 01:26:37,320
让我……下注吧!
Let me... Place your bets!

1734
01:26:37,320 --> 01:26:37,820
呆在那里。
Stay there.

1735
01:26:37,820 --> 01:26:38,380
抓住你的马鞍。
Hold your saddle.

1736
01:26:38,380 --> 01:26:39,310
我不会让他们伤害你的。
I won't let them hurt you.

1737
01:26:39,310 --> 01:26:40,300
来吧，萨利。
Come on, Solly.

1738
01:26:40,300 --> 01:26:41,290
八是赢家!
Eight's the winner!

1739
01:26:43,720 --> 01:26:45,040
这是被陷害的。
This thing's a frame-up.

1740
01:26:45,040 --> 01:26:46,070
你怎么猜到的?
How'd you guess?

1741
01:26:46,070 --> 01:26:48,060
根据我的日程安排，警察来了。
And according to my schedule, here come the police.

1742
01:26:48,060 --> 01:26:49,560
这个地方被洗劫了!
The joint is raided!

1743
01:26:49,560 --> 01:26:51,420
先生，你看到我的自行车了吗?
Please, sir, did you see my bicycle?

1744
01:26:51,420 --> 01:26:52,610
我会给你买一个新的。来吧，伙计们!
I'll buy you a new one. Come on, men!

1745
01:26:52,610 --> 01:26:53,110
来吧，孩子们。
Come on, boys.

1746
01:26:53,110 --> 01:26:54,990
就是它了!
This is it!

1747
01:26:54,990 --> 01:26:55,530
这是突袭!
This is a raid!

1748
01:26:55,530 --> 01:26:56,030
好吧,男孩。
OK, boys.

1749
01:26:56,030 --> 01:26:57,470
站在原地!
Stand where you are!

1750
01:26:59,910 --> 01:27:00,860
哦，这太棒了。
Oh, this is great.

1751
01:27:00,860 --> 01:27:01,830
我让你当船长。
I'll make you a captain.

1752
01:27:01,830 --> 01:27:02,790
我是船长。
I am a captain.

1753
01:27:02,790 --> 01:27:06,170
好的，海军上将。
OK, an admiral.

1754
01:27:06,170 --> 01:27:11,050
慕斯，你又因为开赌场被捕了。
Moose, you're under arrest for running a gambling joint again.

1755
01:27:11,050 --> 01:27:12,230
这不是赌博场所。
This isn't a gambling joint.

1756
01:27:12,230 --> 01:27:14,150
这是一个…这是一个旧娃娃之家。
It's a... it's an old dolls' home.

1757
01:27:14,150 --> 01:27:15,230
你在开玩笑吗?
Are you kidding?

1758
01:27:15,230 --> 01:27:16,760
把它们拿出来。
Take them out.

1759
01:27:16,760 --> 01:27:17,960
现在，稍等一下!
Now, just a minute!

1760
01:27:17,960 --> 01:27:21,220
什么……你以为你要去哪里?
What... Where do you think you're going?

1761
01:27:21,220 --> 01:27:22,250
好吧，我要走了。
Well, I'm getting out of here.

1762
01:27:22,250 --> 01:27:23,090
这地方不是我的。
I don't own this place.

1763
01:27:23,090 --> 01:27:24,720
你不能把任何罪名栽赃给我。
You can't pin anything on me.

1764
01:27:24,720 --> 01:27:27,980
查理，我们从一开始就在关注你的慈善活动。
Charlie, we've been watching your charity racket From the beginning.

1765
01:27:27,980 --> 01:27:29,940
这笔钱是为奈莉·星期四之家筹集的。
This money was collected for the Nellie Thursday Home.

1766
01:27:29,940 --> 01:27:30,870
这就是它的发展方向。
And that's where it's going.

1767
01:27:30,870 --> 01:27:31,850
逮捕他，警官。
Arrest him, Officer.

1768
01:27:31,850 --> 01:27:35,350
哦，现在有人叫我…嘿，放开我的脚!
Oh, now, somebody call my... hey, let go of my feet!

1769
01:27:35,350 --> 01:27:38,390
我会盯着你的，米尔本先生。
And I'm going to keep an eye on you, Mr. Milburn.

1770
01:27:38,390 --> 01:27:39,350
你不必这么做，法官。
You won't have to, Judge.

1771
01:27:39,350 --> 01:27:40,850
我要改过自新。
I'm turning over a new leaf.

1772
01:27:40,850 --> 01:27:43,940
我再也不会被抓住了。
I'll never be caught again.

1773
01:27:43,940 --> 01:27:47,160
说，谢谢你所做的一切，法官。
Say, thanks for everything, Judge.

1774
01:27:47,160 --> 01:27:50,630
如果你想赢，打给我。
If you ever want a winner, call me.

1775
01:27:50,630 --> 01:27:55,660
女士们先生们还有你们所有人，你们太棒了!
Everybody, ladies and gentlemen and all the rest of you, You were great!

1776
01:27:56,660 --> 01:27:57,970
内莉，成功了。
Nellie, it worked.

1777
01:28:01,150 --> 01:28:03,440
好吗?
Well?

1778
01:28:03,440 --> 01:28:03,940
内莉!
Nellie!

1779
01:28:03,940 --> 01:28:06,300
你丈夫，亨利，他要来了。
Your husband, Henry, he's a-coming.

1780
01:28:06,300 --> 01:28:07,830
他只是从雕像旁边经过!
He's a-just a-passing the statue!

1781
01:28:07,830 --> 01:28:09,210
哦，嗬嗬，就是这个了，各位!
Oh, ho-ho, this is it, everybody!

1782
01:28:09,210 --> 01:28:10,940
古巴，把开关拉开，把桌子搬走。
Goomba, pull the switches and get rid of the tables.

1783
01:28:10,940 --> 01:28:11,880
-是的。-来吧。
- Yeah. - Come on.

1784
01:28:11,880 --> 01:28:11,920
-是的。-来吧。布雷尼，别走开。
- Yeah. - Come on. Brainey, don't go away.

1785
01:28:11,920 --> 01:28:12,650
布雷尼，别走开。
Brainey, don't go away.

1786
01:28:12,650 --> 01:28:13,460
我想和你谈谈。
I want to talk to you.

1787
01:28:22,760 --> 01:28:23,260
内莉。
Nellie.

1788
01:28:26,600 --> 01:28:29,090
欢迎回家，亨利。
Welcome home, Henry.

1789
01:28:29,090 --> 01:28:31,180
哦。
Aw.

1790
01:28:31,180 --> 01:28:33,660
你看起来很漂亮，内莉。
You look very pretty, Nellie.

1791
01:28:33,660 --> 01:28:35,300
很高兴见到你，亨利。
It's nice to see you, Henry.

1792
01:28:35,300 --> 01:28:37,100
亨利，这是柠檬小子。
Henry, this is the Lemon Drop Kid.

1793
01:28:37,100 --> 01:28:38,920
他要为这一切负责。
He's responsible for all this.

1794
01:28:38,920 --> 01:28:39,570
谢谢你,孩子。
Thanks, Kid.

1795
01:28:39,570 --> 01:28:40,520
哦，这是可扣除的。
Oh, it's deductible.

1796
01:28:40,520 --> 01:28:41,310
进来吧，汉克。
Come on in, Hank.

1797
01:28:49,690 --> 01:28:52,680
这是我们的贵宾，亨利·里根夫妇。
Here's our guests of honor, Mr. And Mrs. Henry Regan.

1798
01:28:55,590 --> 01:28:56,680
快12点了。
It's almost 12 o'clock.

1799
01:28:56,680 --> 01:28:58,010
该上冰淇淋了。
Time to serve the ice cream.

1800
01:28:58,010 --> 01:28:59,650
我去拿餐巾纸和盘子。
I'll get the napkins and the dishes.

1801
01:28:59,650 --> 01:29:00,860
你真棒。
Goody for you.

1802
01:29:00,860 --> 01:29:01,820
这是你的派对，内莉。
It's your party, Nellie.

1803
01:29:01,820 --> 01:29:03,110
过来切蛋糕。
Come and cut the cake.

1804
01:29:03,110 --> 01:29:04,590
银器在哪里?
Where is the silverware?

1805
01:29:04,590 --> 01:29:06,520
外科医生山姆说它在保险箱里。
Sam the Surgeon said it was in the safe.

1806
01:29:06,520 --> 01:29:07,760
我们怎么把它弄出来?
How do we get it out?

1807
01:29:07,760 --> 01:29:09,520
从保险柜里出来?
Out of the safe?

1808
01:29:09,520 --> 01:29:12,280
是啊，我们怎么把它从保险箱里拿出来?
Yeah, how do we get it out of the safe?

1809
01:29:12,280 --> 01:29:13,270
保险箱里。
The safe.

1810
01:29:20,550 --> 01:29:22,200
哦,不。
Oh, no.

1811
01:29:22,200 --> 01:29:23,080
不是我。
Not me.

1812
01:29:23,080 --> 01:29:24,650
但这是内奸，亨利。
But it's an inside job, Henry.

1813
01:29:24,650 --> 01:29:25,850
什么是非法的。
Nothing illegal.

1814
01:29:25,850 --> 01:29:27,270
算是客人拍的。
Sort of a guest shot.

1815
01:29:27,270 --> 01:29:29,510
我刚因为非法开锁坐了二十年牢。
I just did twenty years for safe cracking.

1816
01:29:29,510 --> 01:29:31,420
所以没有银制餐具我们就不能供应冰淇淋。
So we can't serve the ice cream without the silverware.

1817
01:29:31,420 --> 01:29:33,180
这一切都是为了纪念你。
And the whole thing is in your honor.

1818
01:29:33,180 --> 01:29:35,040
再说了，你也不能突然停止。
Besides, you can't stop all of a sudden.

1819
01:29:35,040 --> 01:29:38,080
你必须逐渐减少。
You have to taper off.

1820
01:29:38,080 --> 01:29:42,290
好吧，我得带上我的纪念品。
Well, uh, I'll have to take my keepsakes with me.

1821
01:29:42,290 --> 01:29:43,680
哦，东西在这儿，哈?
Oh, the stuff is here, ha?

1822
01:29:44,490 --> 01:29:46,690
美妙的,亨利。
Wonderful, Henry.

1823
01:29:46,690 --> 01:29:49,570
祝你好运。
Good luck.

1824
01:29:49,570 --> 01:29:51,010
对不起，内莉。
Excuse me a minute, Nellie.

1825
01:29:55,330 --> 01:29:56,250
你现在在忙什么?
What are you up to now?

1826
01:29:56,250 --> 01:29:57,730
我在这里，你在那里。
Oh, I'm up to here, you're up to there.

1827
01:29:57,730 --> 01:29:58,960
多好的赌注啊?
What a parlay, huh?

1828
01:29:58,960 --> 01:30:00,140
拿着电话。
Hold the phone.

1829
01:30:00,140 --> 01:30:02,490
你眼睛里有固定种族的表情。
You've got that fixed race look in your eye.

1830
01:30:02,490 --> 01:30:03,850
你不觉得这很可爱吗?
Don't you see that's lovely?

1831
01:30:03,850 --> 01:30:05,970
天啊，我可以自由结婚了。
God, I'm free to get married.

1832
01:30:05,970 --> 01:30:08,890
可怜的小娃娃，你等了太久了。
Oh, you poor little doll, you've been waiting so long.

1833
01:30:08,890 --> 01:30:10,520
但对你来说是值得的。
But it was worth it to you.

1834
01:30:10,520 --> 01:30:12,380
现在，你难倒我了。
Now, you got me.

1835
01:30:12,380 --> 01:30:13,310
但是我们负担不起。
But we can't afford it.

1836
01:30:13,310 --> 01:30:14,530
我最近没有工作。
I haven't been working lately.

1837
01:30:14,530 --> 01:30:15,150
放松。
Relax.

1838
01:30:15,150 --> 01:30:16,360
我都计划好了。
I have everything planned.

1839
01:30:39,270 --> 01:30:41,070
但是我们要用什么来赚钱呢?
But what are we going to use for money?

1840
01:30:41,070 --> 01:30:43,010
别担心，亲爱的。
Don't worry, honey.

1841
01:30:43,010 --> 01:30:44,350
我要把银器当掉。
I'll hock the silverware.

1842
01:30:57,240 --> 01:30:58,490
安静,Crosby
Quiet, Crosby.

